20Palestine%20that%20did%20not%20become%20part%20of%20Israel%3A%20the%20West%20Bank%20(including%20East%20Jerusalem)%20and%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palquest.org%2Fen%2Fhighlight%2F22473%2Fevolving-infrastructure-palestinian-refugee-camps%5C%22%3ECamps%20were%20built%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20house%20those%20with%20nowhere%20else%20to%20go.%20Jenin%20was%20one%20such%20camp%2C%20predominantly%20sheltering%20refugees%20from%20Haifa%20and%20Nazareth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%201948%2C%20the%20UN%20passed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigitallibrary.un.org%2Frecord%2F210025%3Fln%3Den%5C%22%3EResolution%20194%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20calling%20for%20the%20refugees%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20at%20the%20earliest%20opportunity.%20Successive%20Israeli%20governments%20consistently%20opposed%20this%2C%20and%20with%20no%20resolution%2C%20the%20refugees%20have%20remained%20in%20exile%20and%20in%20limbo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%202023%20and%20Jenin%20has%20now%20sheltered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2Fwhere-we-work%2Fwest-bank%2Fjenin-camp%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20three%20generations%20of%20refugees%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20home%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F7%2F4%2Fpalestinians-in-jenin-camp-from-nakba-to-israels-latest-assault%5C%22%3Emore%20than%2014%2C000%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20surviving%20on%20less%20than%20half%20a%20square%20kilometre%20of%20land.%20When%20up%20to%204%2C000%20Palestinians%20were%20displaced%20from%20the%20camp%20this%20week%2C%20they%20became%20refugees%20twice%20over.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20this%20has%20happened%20%E2%80%93%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondoweiss.net%2F2022%2F04%2Fremembering-jenin-20-years-after-in-the-shadow-of-ukraine%2F%5C%22%3Eprevious%20attack%20on%20Jenin%20in%202002%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Fd