s%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChatGPT's%20new%20Code%20Interpreter%20tool%20was%20released%20to%20paying%20customers%20on%207%20July.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20Wharton%20professor%20said%3A%20'Things%20that%20took%20me%20weeks%20to%20master%20in%20my%20Ph.D.%20were%20completed%20in%20seconds'%20by%20the%20tool.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEven%20without%20Code%20Interpreter%2C%20ChatGPT%20already%20had%20some%20code-writing%20abilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT's%20newest%20feature%20%E2%80%94%20a%20new%20plugin%20for%20writing%20code%20%E2%80%94%20is%20marking%20%26quot%3Bthe%20strongest%20case%20yet%20for%20a%20future%20where%20AI%20is%20a%20valuable%20companion%20for%20sophisticated%20knowledge%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20Wharton%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oneusefulthing.org%2Fp%2Fwhat-ai-can-do-with-a-toolbox-getting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20published%20on%20Friday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ethan%20Mollick%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmgmt.wharton.upenn.edu%2Fprofile%2Femollick%2F%23overview%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmgmt.wharton.upenn.edu%2Fprofile%2Femollick%2F%23overview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eassociate%20professor%20of%20management%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20detailed%20his%20first%20impressions%20of%20using%20Code%20Interpreter%20to%20write%20code%2C%20perform%20complex%20calculations%2C%20and%20generate%20charts%20%E2%80%94%20saying%20this%20new%20tool%20made%20ChatGPT%20an%20effective%20data%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20that%20took%20me%20weeks%20to%20master%20in%20my%20PhD%20were%20completed%20in%20seconds%20by%20the%20AI%2C%20and%20there%20were%20generally%20fewer%20errors%20than%20I%20would%20expect%20from%20a%20human%20analyst%2C%26quot%3B%20Mollick%20w