aughters%20grew%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jumma%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20them%20to%20study%2C%20but%20they%20said%20%E2%80%98mother%20how%20will%20you%20feed%20us%20alone%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20decided%20to%20come%20to%20work%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20only%20means%20of%20livelihood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20prolonged%20exposure%20to%20dust%2C%20Jumma%20wakes%20up%20with%20a%20headache%20and%20chest%20pain%20on%20most%20days.%20Despite%20the%20health%20problems%2C%20she%20goes%20to%20work%20as%20she%20sees%20no%20other%20option%20to%20feed%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142228%2F66157206_906.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221110%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142228%2F66157206_906.jpg%201110w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142228%2F66157206_906-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142228%2F66157206_906-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662477%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22624%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJumma%20has%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20silicosis%2C%20a%20deadly%20and%20incurable%20lung%20disease%20caused%20by%20the%20inhalation%20of%20the%20silica%20dust.%20Photo%3A%20Sharique%20Ahmad%2FDW%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20not%20alone.%20Her%20neighbor%2C%2038-year-old%20Kaushalya%20Bai%2C%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20three%20years%20ago.%20She%20was%20only%2016%20years%20old%20when%20she%20started%20working%20in%20these%20vast%20sandstone%20mines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20now%20chronically%20ill%20and%20looks%20frail.%20The%20disease%20left%20her%20struggling%20to%20speak.%20The%20doctors%20advised%20her%20to%20stop%20working%20on%20stone%20and%20stay%20away%20from%20dust%2C%20but%20she%20still%20goes%20to%20the%20mine%20three%20days%20a%20week%20as%20she%20has%20four%20children%20to%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20her%20eldest%20son%20Mahaveer%2C%2016%2C%20has%20taken%20on%20the%20responsibility%20of%20supporting%20his%20sick%20mother%20and%20the%20family.%20He%20dropped%20out%20of%20school%20and%20now%20works%20as%20a%20full-time%20miner.%20Kaushalya%20Bai%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20Kanhaiya%20Lal%2C%20also%20died%20of%20a%20lung%20disease%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20sandstone%20hub%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20of%20Budhpura%2C%20located%20in%20the%20northwestern%20state%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20is%20the%20epicenter%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia%2Ft-18996071%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20sandstone%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20here%20died%20one%20after%20another%20after%20toiling%20in%20the%20expansive%20sandstone%20mines%20and%20inhaling%20silica%20dust%20found%20in%20rock%2C%20sand%20and%20quartz%20every%20day%C2%A0until%20they%20were%20eventually%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20time%20passed%2C%20almost%20the%20entire%20male%20population%20of%20Budhpura%20succumbed%20to%20this%20disease.%20Today%2C%20this%20place%20is%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvillage%20of%20widows.%E2%80%9D%20But%20the%20tragedy%20does%20not%20end%20there.%20With%20no%20other%20employment%20options%20left%2C%20the%20widows%20have%20been%20compelled%20to%20undertake%20the%20same%20tasks%20that%20claimed%20their%20husbands%E2%80%99%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Budhpura%2C%20unregulated%20and%20unsafe%20mines%20are%20thriving%2C%20rights%20groups%20say.%20The%20lack%20of%20health%20safeguards%20is%20a%20concern%20for%20women%20working%20in%20this%20industry%20as%20the%20rights%20of%20workers%20are%20flouted%20and%20laws%20are%20hardly%20enforced%2C%20miners%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20one%20estimate%2C%20there%20are%202.5%20million%20mine%20workers%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20a%20large%20number%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20silicosis.%20However%2C%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20people%20suffering%20from%20the%20disease%20remains%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20prominent%20hub%20for%20sandstone%20exports%20to%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2040-page%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9CBlood%20Stone%202022%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Germany%20as%20one%20of%20the%20top%2010%20countries%20that%20import%20sandstone%C2%A0from%20India.%20The%20report%20was%20exclusively%20shared%20with%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20the%20Mine%20Labor%20Protection%20Campaign%20(MLPC)%2C%20a%20non-profit%20that%20advocates%20for%20mine%20workers%E2%80%99%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20estimates%20the%20value%20of%20sandstone%20exports%20from%20India%20to%20Germany%20at%20%244.43%20million%20(%E2%82%AC4.06%20million)%20in%202021-2022%2C%20slightly%20down%20from%20%244.83%20million%20from%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Kingdom%20is%20the%20top%20importer%20of%20Indian%20sandstone%2C%20according%20to%20the%20MLPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFight%20for%20stricter%20regulations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMK%20Devarajan%2C%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20State%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%2C%20spent%20many%20years%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20and%20safety%20of%20mine%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20tenure%2C%20he%20urged%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20Director%20General%20of%20Mines%20Safety%20(DGMS)%2C%20who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20mine%20worker%20welfare%2C%20to%20tighten%20the%20rules%20by%20canceling%20licenses%20of%20those%20who%20flout%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevarajan%20also%20helped%20formulate%20the%20state%20policy%20on%20silicosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142238%2F66157220_906.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221110%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142238%2F66157220_906.jpg%201110w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142238%2F66157220_906-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142238%2F66157220_906-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662478%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22624%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBudhpura%20village%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20prominent%20hub%20for%20sandstone%20exports%20to%20Europe.%20Photo%3A%20Sharique%20Ahmad%2FDW%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20is%20addressing%20the%20health%20issue%20by%20offering%20financial%20compensation%20to%20widows%20and%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20been%20providing%20200%2C000%20rupees%20(%E2%82%AC2%2C218%2C%20%242%2C420)%20as%20compensation%20to%20people%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20and%20300%2C000%20rupees%20(%E2%82%AC3%2C328%2C%20%243%2C632)%20to%20their%20families%20after%20their%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20even%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg.%20The%20problem%20is%20much%20bigger.%20If%20the%20government%20does%20not%20intervene%20properly%2C%20with%20time%20we%20will%20witness%20a%20massive%20increase%20of%20silicosis%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devarajan%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20phone%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20needs%20to%20enforce%20and%20crack%20down%20on%20illegal%20mines%20to%20stop%20this%20crisis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelping%20widows%20to%20secure%20compensation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hundred%20meters%20away%20from%20the%20mining%20site%2C%20the%20non-profit%20MLPC%20was%20organizing%20a%20legal%20camp%20for%20the%20women%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20husbands%20to%20silicosis.%20Dozens%20of%20widows%20gather%20to%20attend%20the%20legal%20camp%20that%20helps%20them%20in%20claiming%20financial%20compensation%20from%20the%20government.%20Some%20of%20the%20widows%20attending%20have%20been%20fighting%20for%20compensation%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20CEO%20Rana%20Sengupta%20headed%20the%20legal%20camp.%20He%20was%20checking%20the%20documents%20of%20widows%20and%20registering%20their%20names.%20His%20team%20of%20lawyers%20was%20preparing%20a%20long%20list%20of%20women%20who%20lost%20their%20husbands%20to%20silicosis.%20He%20said%20that%20getting%20financial%20compensation%20from%20the%20state%20is%20a%20long%20and%20daunting%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20financial%20penalty%20on%20mine%20owners%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%20when%20they%20%5Bminers%5D%20die%20or%20live.%20So%2C%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20wake%20up%20as%20there%20are%20so%20many%20mine%20workers%20who%20have%20died.%20And%20we%20cannot%20bear%20the%20loss%20of%20human%20life%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rana%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogesh%20Gupta%20has%20been%20operating%20mines%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Rajasthan.%20Previously%2C%20he%20owned%20a%20sandstone%20mine%20in%20Budhpur%20village%2C%20but%20he%20has%20since%20closed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20blames%20the%20rise%20of%20unregistered%20and%20unregulated%20mines%20for%20the%20grim%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20unregistered%20and%20unregulated%20workers%20work%20without%20any%20safety%20helmets%20for%20long%20hours.%20The%20rise%20of%20new%20or%20mafia%20mine%20owners%20who%20do%20not%20follow%20any%20regulations%20is%20leading%20to%20this%20massive%20health%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142248%2F66157230_906.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221110%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142248%2F66157230_906.jpg%201110w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142248%2F66157230_906-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10142248%2F66157230_906-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662479%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22624%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDozens%20of%20widows%20gather%20to%20attend%20the%20legal%20camp%20that%20helps%20them%20in%20claiming%20financial%20compensation%20from%20the%20government.%20Photo%3A%20Sharique%20Ahmad%2FDW%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELack%20of%20health%20care%20access%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20village%2C%20dozens%20of%20mine%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20are%20pouring%20into%20the%20local%20hospital%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Bundi%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20There%20were%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20doctors%20attending%20to%20patients%20and%20they%20lacked%20equipment%20that%20could%20be%20used%20to%20diagnose%20or%20treat%20respiratory%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20hospital%20medical%20officer%2C%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Kumar%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20human%20resources%20as%20well%20as%20inadequate%20training%20among%20doctors%20related%20to%20silicosis%20have%20resulted%20in%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20misdiagnoses%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20visit%20to%20the%20facility%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%20was%20examining%20a%20mine%20worker%20who%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20two%20years%20ago%20and%20was%20complaining%20of%20severe%20chest%20pain%20and%20breathlessness.%20The%20doctor%20said%20his%20lungs%20were%20completely%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20hospital%2C%20every%20day%20we%20have%2050-60%20patients%20who%20have%20respiratory%20problems%20and%20among%20them%2050%25%20cases%20are%20of%20those%20who%20are%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis.%20This%20is%20an%20alarming%20disease.%20There%20are%20cases%20which%20have%20reached%20the%20third%20stage%20and%20are%20in%20a%20dangerous%20zone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Jumma%20and%20other%20women%20continue%20to%20risk%20their%20lives%20without%20any%20proper%20support%20or%20protection.%20They%20work%20in%20the%20mines%20despite%20splitting%20headaches%20and%20congested%20lungs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemembering%20her%20husband%2C%20Jumma%20pointed%20towards%20the%20mines%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20see%20these%20mines.%20My%20husband%20fell%20sick%20working%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-lung-disease-turns-budhpura-into-village-of-widows%2Fa-66159058%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.i