%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKo%20got%20his%20free-diving-instructor%20license%20and%20started%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Raymond%20Ko%2C%20a%20free-diving%20instructor%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20about%20leaving%20a%20career%20in%20finance%20behind.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20laid%20off%20three%20times%20in%20my%20career%20and%20fired%20once%2C%20but%20being%20laid%20off%20by%20Deutsche%20Bank%20changed%20my%20life%20for%20the%20better.%20I'm%20no%20longer%20monetarily%20rich%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20true%20wealth%20underwater%20and%20am%20immensely%20grateful%20for%20my%20free-diving%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20roller%20coaster%20of%20a%20work-life%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20fired%20in%202009%20from%20my%20position%20as%20a%20cash-equity%20sales%20trader%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20it%20was%20a%20shock.%20In%202012%2C%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20job%20as%20a%20regional%20sales%20trader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20as%20surprised%20when%20Deutsche%20Bank%20laid%20me%20off%20in%202017.%20I%20returned%20to%20it%20in%202019%2C%20only%20to%20get%20laid%20off%20for%20the%20third%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20fired%20as%20a%20trader%20in%20Taiwan%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201995%2C%20I%20graduated%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20economics%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20spent%20a%20year%20in%20Shanghai%20learning%20Mandarin.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20there%20was%20an%20economic%20boom%20in%20China%2C%20so%20I%20moved%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20investment%20banking.%20Between%201997%20and%201998%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20an%20investment-research%20assistant%20at%20CLSA%20%E2%80%94%20a%20top%20investment%20group%20in%20Asia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%2C%20I%20was%20offered%20a%20position%20in%20Taiwan%20as%20a%20cash-equity%20sales%20trader.%20I%20climbed%20the%20ranks%20for%20about%20four%20years%20and%20was%20making%20%24250%2C000.%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20how%20much%20I%20was%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lived%20in%20Taiwan%20for%20seven%20years.%20I%20got%20married%20and%20had%20two%20kids.%20Even%20before%20I%20was%20fired%2C%20I%20suffered%20from%20anxiety%20and%20panic%20attacks%2C%20but%20I%20convinced%20myself%20I%20was%20happy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20the%20Taiwanese%20economy%20seemed%20shaky%2C%20so%20I%20requested%20a%20transfer%20back%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20worked%20for%20several%20more%20years.%20In%202009%2C%20I%20was%20fired%20suddenly%20from%20my%20position%20as%20a%20cash-equity%20sales%20trader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20shock.%20I%20started%20my%20career%20at%20CLSA%20and%20planned%20to%20end%20it%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20called%20me%20into%20a%20room%20and%20told%20me%20I%20was%20underperforming%2C%20which%20wasn't%20true.%20The%20only%20other%20person%20who%20got%20let%20go%20was%20a%20colleague%20in%20Singapore.%20The%20experience%20was%20brutal%20and%20led%20to%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'd%20worked%20for%20Sanford%20C.%20Bernstein%20for%202%20years%20when%20I%20was%20laid%20off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20secured%20another%20trading%20job%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20Finding%20another%20position%20wasn't%20hard.%20Headhunters%20and%20brokers%20began%20reaching%20out%20to%20me%20immediately.%20I%20was%20working%20again%20within%20four%20months%20of%20getting%20fired.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20have%20started%20earlier%2C%20but%20I'd%20worked%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20needed%20a%20break.%20I%20worked%20briefly%20as%20a%20regional%20sales%20trader%20at%20Execution%20Noble%20from%20January%202010%20to%20September%202010%20before%20starting%20as%20a%20regional%20sales%20trader%20at%20Sanford%20C.%20Bernstein%20in%20October%202010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20over%20two%20years%20later%2C%20I%20was%20laid%20off.%20It%20was%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20before%20Christmas%20and%20one%20of%20the%20scariest%20times%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20sick%20to%20my%20stomach%20thinking%20about%20the%20severe%20financial%20strain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20I%20was%20incredibly%20grateful%20to%20start%20working%20as%20an%20equity%20sales%20trader%20at%20Deutsche%20Bank%20in%20Taiwan.%20I%20was%20earning%20%24255%2C000%20a%20year%20at%20this%20job.%20I%20enjoyed%20my%20time%20there%2C%20and%20my%20coworkers%20and%20boss%20were%20interesting%20and%20fun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20at%20Deutsche%20Bank%2C%20I%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20fibromyalgia%2C%20which%20causes%20chronic%20fatigue%20and%20extreme%20body%20pain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20Deutsche%20Bank%20twice%20in%203%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20laid%20off%20from%20Deutsche%20Bank%20in%20February%202017.%20I%20wasn't%20shocked.%20There%20was%20a%20global%20culling%20of%20directors%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20the%20only%20one%20laid%20off.%20The%20severance%20laws%20in%20Taiwan%20are%20favorable%2C%20and%20I%20was%20very%20pleased%20with%20my%20payout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dabbled%20in%20starting%20an%20e-commerce%20business%20until%20April%202018%2C%20working%20for%20my%20friend's%20startup.%20I%20was%20just%20helping%20out%20until%20a%20better%20opportunity%20came%20along.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20I%20came%20across%20free%20diving%20online%20and%20was%20shocked%20to%20learn%20that%20Taiwan%20was%20a%20free-diving%20mecca.%20I%20signed%20up%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aidainternational.org%2FEducation%2FAIDAFreedivingCourses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAIDA2%20Freediver%3C%2Fa%3E%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20free%20diving%2C%20I%20experienced%20an%20energy%20and%20vibrancy%20I%20hadn't%20felt%20in%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20feel%20the%20pain%20or%20fatigue%20I%20usually%20got%20from%20my%20fibromyalgia%20in%20the%20ocean.%20Working%20full%20time%2C%20I%20could%20dive%20only%20a%20few%20hours%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20returned%20to%20Deutsche%20Bank%20in%20January%202019%20on%20%24220%2C000%20a%20year.%20I%20was%20told%20I%20could%20take%20over%20the%20role%20of%20equity%20head%20if%20I%20did%20well.%20I%20wanted%20to%20end%20my%20career%20as%20the%20head%20of%20equities%20at%20Deutsche%20Bank%20in%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECultivating%20my%20free-diving%20hobby%20saved%20me%20from%20being%20blindsided%20by%20layoffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20trained%20for%20a%20free-diving-instructor%20certification%20over%20the%20weekends.%20I%20planned%20to%20teach%20diving%20as%20a%20fun%20side%20hustle.%20At%20work%2C%20I%20streamed%20free-diving%20videos%20on%20one%20of%20my%20many%20monitors%20%E2%80%94%20I%20dreamed%20of%20the%20ocean%20constantly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20six%20months%20of%20my%20return%20to%20Deutsche%20Bank%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F08%2Finvesting%2Fdeutsche-bank-layoffs%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20my%20entire%20global%20division%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20another%20generous%20severance%20payout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20laid%20off%20again%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20I%20wasn't%20shocked%20and%20upset.%20I%20had%20my%20free%20diving%20to%20fall%20back%20on%2C%20which%20was%20comforting.%20Less%20than%20a%20month%20later%2C%20I%20finished%20my%20instructor%20training%20in%20Indonesia's%20Gili%20Islands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20took%20time%20out%20to%20travel%20before%20starting%20my%20successful%20free-diving%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20July%202019%20and%20November%202020%2C%20my%20girlfriend%20and%20I%20were%20nomadic.%20We%20bounced%20around%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand%3B%20India%3B%20Hong%20Kong%3B%20Taiwan%3B%20and%20Las%20Vegas.%20When%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20we%20headed%20back%20to%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20settling%20back%20into%20life%20in%20Xiaoliuqiu%2C%20I%20landed%20my%20first%20free-diving%20student%20%E2%80%94%20a%20close%20friend.%20Slowly%2C%20I%20built%20my%20business%20through%20word%20of%20mouth%20and%20online%20marketing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20by%20hosting%20one%20three-day%20course%20a%20week%2C%20teaching%20two%20students%20at%20a%20time.%20I%20eventually%20became%20a%20full-time%20free-diving%20instructor%2C%20teaching%20four%20to%20six%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20students%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20but%20I%20advertise%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20many%20students%20find%20me%20on%20my%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20target%20students%20are%20white-collar%20professionals%20stuck%20behind%20a%20desk.%20I%20want%20to%20inspire%20them%20to%20get%20out%20into%20the%20ocean%20for%20their%20mental%20and%20physical%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20turned%2050%2C%20I%20make%20about%20%242%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20and%20I'm%20happier%20than%20ever.%20I'm%20not%20rich%2C%20but%20I'm%20immensely%20grateful%20for%20free%20diving.%20It's%20healed%20my%20fibromyalgia.%20I've%20been%20symptom-free%20for%20two%20years%2C%20and%20in%20that%20time%2C%20I've%20not%20suffered%20any%20panic%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeutsche-bank-employee-laid-off-happier-than-ever-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688979833000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64abca3f8ed31300199e3e8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeutsche-bank-employee-laid-off-happier-than-ever-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ra