0to%20understand%20how%20we%20could%20build%20more%20responsible%20technology%20products%20that%20respected%20people's%20privacy%2C%20which%20was%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%20at%20the%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeta%3A%20Product%20marketing%20manager%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%24150%2C000%20base%20salary%20%2B%20%2415K%20target%20bonus%20%2B%20%2480K%20over%204%20years%20stock%20package%20%2B%20%2420K%20sign-on%20bonus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20I%20was%20contacted%20by%20Meta%20to%20join%20their%20privacy%20product%20marketing%20team%20for%20their%20new%20augmented%20reality%20and%20virtual%20reality%20products.%20I%20applied%20and%20successfully%20got%20the%20role%2C%20which%20provided%20me%20with%20exposure%20to%20early%20product%20development.%C2%A0%20I%20aggressively%20negotiated%20the%20salary%20and%20also%20secured%20a%20promotion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20joining%20Meta%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20receive%20another%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20time%20there%2C%20I%20took%20on%20various%20roles%2C%20starting%20with%20building%20the%20privacy%20product%20marketing%20team%20for%20augmented%20reality%20and%20virtual%20reality%20products.%20That%20was%20an%20exciting%20time%20as%20VR%20was%20gaining%20popularity%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%20and%20people%20staying%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20emerging%20technology%20and%20I%20got%20to%20work%20on%20some%20really%20cool%20early%20product%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20follow%20a%20respected%20manager%20and%20underwent%20an%20internal%20transfer%20to%20a%20new%20team.%20This%20role%20became%20my%20personal%20%26quot%3Bmini%20MBA%26quot%3B%20as%20I%20gained%20extensive%20knowledge%20in%20different%20aspects%20of%20the%20business%2C%20including%20long-term%20product%20roadmap%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20category%20m