Job%20hopping%20helped%20me%20realize%20what%20I%20did%20and%20didn't%20like%2C%20and%20I%20made%20career%20moves%20accordingly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20my%2020s%20was%20my%20time%20to%20explore%20different%20roles%20and%20industries.%20Our%20careers%20span%20upwards%20of%2040%20years%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20full%20advantage%20of%20exploring%20%E2%80%94%20I%20feel%20the%20later%20you%20get%20in%20your%20career%2C%20the%20harder%20it%20is%20to%20drop%20off%20and%20do%20something%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20become%20more%20senior%2C%20the%20company%20values%20more%20depth%20and%20progression.%20They%20want%20to%20see%20that%20you%20can%20stay%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20to%20sum%20up%20the%20biggest%20learning%20out%20of%20my%20short%2C%20six-year%20career%2C%20it's%20to%20not%20be%20afraid%20of%20change%20and%20take%20a%20chance%20on%20yourself%20%E2%80%94%20trust%20that%20everything%20is%20going%20to%20work%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you'd%20like%20to%20share%20your%20salary%20journey%2C%20email%20Aria%20Yang%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aayang%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eayang%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-salary-google-meta-linkedin-how-much-i-made-career-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688979600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a831016d7e02001af87448%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-salary-google-meta-linkedin-how-much-i-made-career-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mitchie%20Nguyen%20spent%20six%20years%20working%20in%20Big%20Tech%20and%20shares%20her%20exact%20salary%20including%20base%2C%20bonuses%2C%20stock%20packages%2C%20and%20sign-on%20bonuses.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22http%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22