s%20possible%20when%20you%20do%20good%20work%2C%20pay%20attention%20to%20company%20trends%2C%20and%20have%20good%20leadership%20that%20recognizes%20your%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20my%20manager%20and%20my%20organization's%20HR%20business%20partner%20on%20February%2013%2C%20they%20notified%20me%20that%20%26quot%3Bmy%20skills%20were%20no%20longer%20required%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20my%20last%20day%20would%20be%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20especially%20painful%20to%20me%20was%20that%20our%20CEO%20had%20announced%20in%20late%20January%20that%20a%20small%20layoff%20would%20be%20coming%2C%20and%20that%20several%20weeks%20would%20pass%20until%20affected%20people%20would%20start%20to%20be%20notified.%20Imagine%20sitting%20around%20wondering%20if%20the%20hammer%20is%20going%20to%20fall%20on%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20felt%20paralyzed%20when%20my%20worst%20fears%20were%20confirmed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20an%20interim%20period%20to%20find%20another%20role%20in%20the%20company%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-sweeping-the-us-these-are-the-companies-making-cuts-2023%23sap-up-to-3000-positions-56%5C%22%3Ebe%20laid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20given%20a%20%26quot%3Bcode%26quot%3B%20to%20use%20in%20our%20internal%20job-search%20tool%20so%20I%20could%20get%20%26quot%3Bpriority%26quot%3B%20consideration.%20Even%20with%20the%20code%2C%20the%20hiring%20manager%20responsible%20for%20a%20role%20I%20was%20very%20qualified%20for%20rejected%20me%20within%20hours.%20If%20they'd%20wanted%20to%20keep%20me%2C%20they%20could%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20severance%20package%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20typical%2C%20but%20not%20the%20best%2C%20for%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20included%20severance%20pay%20based%20on%20years%20of%20service%2C%20cash%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-get-cobra-health-insurance%5C%22%3ECOBRA%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20continue%20health%20insurance%2C%20and%20a%20payout%20for%20unused%20vacation%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20offered%20support%20services%20for%20displaced%20workers%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lhh.com%2Fau%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELee%20Hecht%20Harrison%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20talent-acquisition%20and%20job-recruitment%20firm%2C%20which%20have%20been%20tremendously%20helpful.%20They%20assigned%20me%20a%20coach%20who%20made%20herself%20available%20as%20often%20as%20I%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20paralyzed%20me%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20I%20couldn't%20even%20read%20%E2%80%94%20it%20took%20too%20much%20brainpower%20to%20process%20the%20words.%20I%20spent%20my%20daytime%20hours%20crying%20and%20bingeing%20%26quot%3BAnd%20Just%20Like%20That%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Morning%20Show.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20a%20job%20became%20my%20full-time%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%20for%20a%20total%20of%20134%20jobs%2C%20and%20all%20of%20them%20were%20for%20talent-development%20or%20learning-and-development%20leadership%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20repeatedly%20frustrating%20when%20you%20%26quot%3Btick%20every%20box%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20skills%20gained%20through%20experience%20but%20can't%20get%20a%20first%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20places%20even%20ghosted%20me.%20That's%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise%20%E2%80%94%20if%20your%20automated%20system%20can't%20even%20generate%20a%20rejection%20letter%2C%20shame%20on%20you%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20work%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20applying%20for%20jobs%2C%20I%20had%20plenty%20of%20moments%20to%20clear%20my%20thinking%20and%20find%20a%20way%20forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20growing%20restless%20for%20years%2C%20and%20I%20had%20considered%20podcasting%2C%20writing%2C%20and%20cons