s-development%20aspect%20of%20being%20out%20on%20my%20own.%20My%20new%20job%20is%2040%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20and%20I%20work%20on%20my%20business%20during%20nights%20and%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20podcast%20and%20business%20are%20no%20longer%20just%20dreams%20%E2%80%94%20I%20have%20a%20focus%20and%20a%20plan%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20many%20people%20who%20told%20me%20that%20similar%20experiences%20brought%20about%20the%20best%20changes%20in%20their%20lives%2C%20I%20didn't%20believe%20it%20back%20when%20I%20was%20gasping%20for%20air%20while%20ugly%20crying%2C%20but%20I%20definitely%20believe%20it%20now.%20While%20this%20is%20somewhat%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bcautionary%20tale%2C%26quot%3B%20I'm%20in%20no%20way%20bitter%20about%20my%20layoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20is%20to%20take%20the%20time%20to%20update%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20LinkedIn%20profile%20monthly%20because%20you%20never%20know%20when%20you'll%20need%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20if%20you%20find%20yourself%20in%20this%20situation%2C%20process%20your%20layoff%2C%20but%20don't%20take%20too%20much%20time.%20Don't%20be%20bitter%2C%20and%20don't%20take%20it%20personally%20%E2%80%94%20it%20isn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-own-business-layoff-sap-happier-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688979600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a727cb4cc8540019cba747%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-own-business-layoff-sap-happier-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Barbara%20Jamelli-Sefchik's%20layoff%20left%20her%20frozen%20for%20days%2C%20but%20it%20gave%20her%20time%20to%20taste%20what's%20possible%20when%20she's%20free%20to%20do%20what%20she's%20good%20at.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22http%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Robin%20Madell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2