%2C%20my%20mannerisms%20began%20to%20look%20like%20those%20of%20a%20girl.%20I%20liked%20being%20a%20girl.%20It%20was%20what%20my%20body%20was%20making%20me%20do%2C%20making%20me%20walk%20like%20a%20girl%2C%20talk%20like%20a%20girl%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSociety%20told%20me%20that%20I%20was%20different.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhydal%20realised%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20police%20officer%20after%20working%20as%20a%20security%20guard.%20She%20applied%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20police%20force%20in%202022%2C%20but%20she%20found%20there%20was%20no%20third%20gender%20category.%20She%20was%20also%20not%20allowed%20to%20apply%20under%20the%20female%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhydal%20and%20several%20other%20transgender%20individuals%20then%20approached%20an%20administrative%20tribunal%2C%20which%20ordered%20the%20state%20to%20create%20a%20provision%20for%20transgenders%20in%20the%20recruitment%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20department%20went%20to%20court%20against%20the%20order%2C%20saying%20that%20we%20were%20not%20capable%20for%20police%20recruitment.%20Our%20lawyer%20argued%20how%20can%20we%20be%20deemed%20incapable%20without%20being%20examined%20and%20without%20taking%20our%20physical%20and%20written%20exams%3F%20The%20High%20Court%20ruled%20in%20our%20favor%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETransgender%20applicants%20encounter%20many%20obstacles%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findias-first-transgender-school-opens-but-discrimination-remains%2Fa-36986873%5C%22%3Etransgender%20people%C2%A0were%20permitted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20fill%20out%20the%20recruitment%20form.%20However%2C%20the%20process%20was%20not%20easy.%20Mukhydal%20said%20they%20were%20given%20only%20five%20days%20to%20finish%20the%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20that%2C%2073%20transgender%20people%20filled%20out%20the%20forms.%20But%20if%20this%20time%20frame%20would%20have%20been%20a%20month%20long%2C%20maybe%201%2C000%20applications%20would%20have%20come%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20then%20given%20three%20months%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20physical%20standards%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20attitude%20of%20the%20government%20was%20negative%20toward%20us.%20They%20had%20already%20decided%20that%20we%20were%20not%20capable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhydal%20passed%20the%20physical%20test.%20However%2C%20she%20was%20dismayed%20to%20see%20that%20her%20name%2C%20along%20with%20other%20transgender%20applicants%2C%20was%20listed%20in%20the%20female%20column%2C%20despite%20having%20spent%20time%20and%20effort%20to%20have%20a%20third%20gender%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20for%20the%20written%20test%2C%20the%20transgender%20group%20ended%20up%20being%20included%20with%20male%20and%20female%20groups%2C%20both%20of%20which%20had%20more%20time%20to%20prepare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20disqualified%20because%20we%20could%20not%20compete%20with%20people%20in%20those%20general%20categories%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2035%20years%20old%2C%20Mukhydal%20is%20at%20the%20age%20limit%20in%20Maharashtra%20for%20applying%20to%20the%20police%20force.%20She%20feels%20that%20had%20it%20not%20been%20for%20the%20overly%20complicated%20bureaucracy%2C%20she%20would%20have%20been%20accepted.%20However%2C%20this%20will%20not%20keep%20her%20from%20campaigning%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20others%20who%20face%20similar%20obstacles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findian-supreme-court-recognizes-transgender-people%2Fa-17567329%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20top%20court%20ruled%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20transgender%20community%20would%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20third%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20also%20ordered%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20a%20quota%20of%201%25%20for%20transgender%20persons%20to%20be%20included%20in%20jobs%20and%20education%2C%20which%20is%20a%20similar%20percentage%20in%20line%20with%20other%20minority%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransgender%20groups%20across%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia%2Ft-18996071%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20this%201%25%20quota.%20However%2C%20so%20far%2C%20only%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Karnataka%20has%20implemented%20the%201%25%20reservation%20for%20transgender%20people%20in%20public%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETransgender%20community%20motivated%20for%20public%20service%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20central%20state%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%2013%20transgender%20people%20were%20recruited%20by%20the%20police%20force%20in%202021.%20Nine%20transgender%20people%20are%20now%20part%20of%20a%20specialized%20unit%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Police%20that%20is%20deployed%20in%20Maoist-insurgency%20hit%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20undergoing%20specialized%20general%20warfare%20training.%20They%20are%20doing%20fairly%20well.%20They%20are%20quite%20motivated.%20And%20their%20morale%20after%20joining%20the%20force%20is%20very%20high%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20official%20from%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Police%20told%20DW%2C%20under%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20move%20has%20also%20made%20the%20force%20more%20inclusive%20and%20more%20sensitive.%20It%20is%20expected%20from%20the%20police%20force%20to%20be%20impartial%20and%20sensitive.%20That%20impartiality%20and%20sensitivity%20is%20more%20visible%20if%20you%20include%20all%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20official%20said%20the%20police%20department%20has%20welcomed%20the%20transgender%20persons%20in%20its%20ranks%2C%20even%20if%20there%20is%20extra%20work%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20have%20included%20the%20third%20gender%2C%20the%20force%20should%20be%20sensitized%20so%20that%20there%20is%20no%20discrimination%20within%20the%20forces.%20People%20in%20the%20police%20forces%20also%20belong%20to%20the%20same%20society%20as%20the%20third%20gender.%20Now%2C%20you%20are%20in%20the%20same%20force%2C%20you%20have%20to%20do%20the%20duty%20together%2C%20shoulder-to-shoulder%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20any%20complaints%2C%20but%20admitted%20there%20may%20be%20complications%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20could%20be%20a%20few%20challenges%20like%20separate%20restrooms%20or%20barracks.%20Until%20now%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20come%20up%2C%20but%20these%20are%20a%20few%20challenges%20that%20I%20foresee.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20numbers%20of%20transgender%20people%20are%20very%20small%2C%20once%20the%20numbers%20grow%20then%20there%20could%20be%20a%20possibility%20of%20these%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhydal%20believes%20that%20when%20transgender%20people%20are%20allowed%20into%20government%20jobs%2C%20equality%20will%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20change%20would%20be%20that%20transgender%20people%20would%20able%20to%20break%20away%20from%20the%20means%20of%20income%20like%20begging%20and%20sex%20work.%20Once%20we%20start%20getting%20government%20jobs%2C%20our%20future%20generations%20will%20see%20that%20there%20are%20other%20options%20and%20a%20life%20of%20respect%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findias-transgender-people-demand-inclusion-in-police-forces%2Fa-66082597%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ci