ndia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flife-threatening-flooding-overwhelms-new-york-roadways-killing-1-person%2Famp_articleshow%2F101633689.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flife-threatening-flooding-overwhelms-new-york-roadways-killing-1-person%2Famp_articleshow%2F101633689.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20Paper%20Leak%20Scandal%20Is%20at%20Risk%20of%20Being%20Lost%20Without%20Resolution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10134006%2FFpV7xVpaUAEHEcH.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20that%20is%20worrying%20the%20majority%20of%20Arunachalees%20is%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(APPSC)%20paper%20leak%20scandal%20going%20the%20Rs%201%2C000-crore%20PDS%20scandal%20way.%20In%202004%2C%20when%20the%20PDS%20scam%20was%20first%20exposed%2C%20it%20had%20rocked%20the%20state.%20The%20SIC%20investigated%20the%20cases%20and%20some%20arrests%20were%20made%20by%20it.%20Interestingly%2C%20Mayank%20Sheel%20Chohan%2C%20a%201998-batch%20UT%20cadre%20IPS%20officer%20who%20had%20headed%20the%20SIC%20for%20a%20long%20time%20when%20the%20PDS%20scam%20was%20investigated%2C%20was%20sacked%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20in%202017%20after%20he%20was%20found%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20fit%E2%80%9D%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20service%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnon-performance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20almost%20everyone%20seems%20to%20have%20forgotten%20this%20case.%20The%20last%20time%20the%20PDS%20scam%20was%20in%20the%20news%20was%20probably%20in%20December%202017%2C%20when%20in%20a%20tweet%20chief%20minister%20Pema%20Khandu%20announced%20that%20he%20had%20recommended%20the%20multi-crore%20PDS%20scam%20case%20to%20the%20CBI%20for%20investigation.%20Not%20much%20has%20been%20heard%20about%20the%20case%20since%20then.%20Apart%20from%20making%20a%20few%20arrests%2C%20the%20case%20did%20not%20see%20any%20particular%20outcome.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20certain%20cases%2C%20there%20was%20allegation%20of%20this%20case%20being%20misused%20to%20target%20political%20opponents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APPSC%20paper%20scandal%20came%20into%20public%20limelight%20when%20whistleblower%20late%20Gyamar%20Padang%20exposed%20the%20deep%20rooted%20corrupt%20nexus%20that%20prevailed%20in%20the%20commission.%20The%20scandal%20hit%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20youths%20have%20been%20left%20deeply%20frustrated%20and%20angry.%20The%20SIC%2C%20which%20first%20investigated%20the%20case%2C%20made%20several%20arrests%2C%20including%20many%20serving%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20due%20to%20the%20demand%20placed%20by%20several%20groups%2C%20including%20the%20Pan%20Arunachal%20Joint%20Steering%20Committee%20(PAJSC)%2C%20which%20was%20spearheading%20the%20movement%20against%20the%20APPSC%20paper%20leak%20scandal%2C%20the%20state%20government%20handed%20over%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20the%20CBI%20took%20over%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(APPSC)%20assistant%20engineer%20examination%20question%20paper%20leak%20case.%20It%20registered%20an%20FIR%20and%20started%20an%20investigation.%20Later%2C%20all%20cases%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI.%20Since%20the%20premier%20investigation%20agency%20took%20over%20the%20case%2C%20there%20has%20not%20been%20any%20major%20development.%20With%20the%20CBI%20mostly%20operating%20from%20Guwahati%2C%20the%20information%20source%20has%20dried%20up.%20Also%2C%20the%20name%20of%20one%20of%20the%20SIC%20officials%2C%20Bumcho%20Krong%2C%20who%20was%20initially%20deputed%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20got%20dragged%20into%20the%20mysterious%20death%20of%20former%20APPSC%20official%20Tumi%20Gangkak.%20This%20also%20affected%20the%20pace%20of%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20many%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20PAJSC%20were%20either%20arrested%20or%20under%20the%20radar%20of%20the%20police%20for%20their%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%2072-hour%20bandh%20call.%20The%20faces%20of%20PAJSC%20%E2%80%93%20Techi%20Puru%20and%20Tadak%20Nalo%20%E2%80%93%20were%20on%20the%20run%20for%20a%20long%20time%20after%20the%20police%20had%20booked%20them%20under%20the%20APUAPA.%20Since%20then%20they%20have%20got%20reprieve%20from%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20this%20whole%20episode%20has%20hurt%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20PAJSC%20members%20and%20the%20movement%20is%20slowly%20losing%20steam.%20Truly%20speaking%2C%20the%20movement%20started%20to%20take%20the%20wrong%20turn%20when%20people%20with%20dubious%20characters%20started%20to%20hijack%20the%20movement.%20Most%20of%20these%20people%20were%20mostly%20concerned%20about%20themselves%20and%20not%20the%20APPSC%20scandal%20in%20the%20true%20sense.%20Their%20press%20briefings%20were%20mostly%20like%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ehum%20yeh%2C%20hum%20woh%2C%20hum%20usse%20nahi%20darta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%20Instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20characters%20became%20the%20centre%20of%20attention%20and%20this%20is%20when%20movement%20started%20to%20lose%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20this%2C%20one%20cannot%20deny%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20PAJSC%20for%20a%20long%20time%20ran%20a%20very%20successful%20anti-corruption%20movement%20and%20captured%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20entire%20Arunachal.%20People%20saw%20hope%20in%20it%20and%20the%20government%20feared%20it.%20Perhaps%20it%20went%20wrong%20somewhere%20and%20hopefully%20they%20will%20introspect.%20If%20the%20APPSC%20paper%20leak%20scandal%20has%20to%20reach%20a%20logical%20conclusion%2C%20the%20PAJSC%20will%20have%20to%20revive%20and%20restart%20the%20fight.%20Or%20else%20this%20will%20become%20the%20next%20PDS%20scandal%20and%20will%20be%20lost%20in%20oblivion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2023%2F07%2F10%2Fis-the-appsc-paper-leak-scandal-turning-into-the-next-pds-scam%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2F%5C%22%3EArunachal%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688977792000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10134006%2FFpV7xVpaUAEHEcH.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Farunachal-pradesh-paper-leak-scandal-resolution%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Like%20the%20multi-crore%20PDS%20scam%20case%20before%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20APPSC%20paper%20leak%20will%20not%20reach%20its%20logical%20conclusion.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22https%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Farunachal-pradesh-paper-leak-scandal-resolution%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anushka%20Sharma%20turns%20down%20Jee%20Le%20Zara!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688977231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101633341%2Cimgsize-15626.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanushka-sharma-turns-down-jee-le-zara%2Farticleshow%2F101633370.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101633370.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAfter%20Priyanka%20Chopra%20Jonas%20stepped%20away%20from%20Farhan%20Akhtar's%20Jee%20Le%20Zara%20also%20starrign%20Katrina%20Kaif%20and%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20there%20was%20a%20bzz%20that%20makers%20would%20be%20approaching%20Anushka%20Sharma%20for%20the%20same%20role.%20But%20it%20seem%20that%20Anushka%20has%2