s.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fat-delhis-connaught-place-road-turns-river%2Farticleshow%2F101632771.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20the%20national%20capital%20broke%20a%2041-year%20rainfall%20record%20by%20logging%20153mm%20of%20rain%20in%20the%2024-hour%20period%20ending%20on%208.30am%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Delhi%20continued%20to%20receive%20heavy%20showers%20in%20the%20day%20leaving%20several%20areas%20flooded.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22http%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fat-delhis-connaught-place-road-turns-river%2Farticleshow%2F101632771.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Case%20Registered%20Against%20Fact-Finding%20Team%20Which%20Said%20Violence%20Was%20'State-Sponsored'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20three%20members%20of%20a%20fact-finding%20team%20which%20visited%20Manipur%20recently%20and%20declared%20that%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20the%20state%20were%20the%20result%20of%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20registered%20on%20July%208%20at%20the%20Imphal%20police%20station%20against%20Annie%20Raja%2C%20Nisha%20Siddhu%20and%20Deeksha%20Dwivedi.%20The%20three%20women%20were%20part%20of%20a%20the%20National%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%20(NFIW)%E2%80%99s%20fact-finding%20team%20that%20visited%20Manipur%20from%20June%2028%20to%20July%201.%20Raja%20is%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20NFIW%20while%20Sidhu%20is%20its%20national%20secretary.%20Dwivedi%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20FIR%20invokes%20several%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20state%2C%20provocation%20and%20defamation.%20The%20complaint%20was%20filed%20by%20one%20L.%20Liben%20Singh%20for%20statements%20made%20by%20the%20three%20women%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20where%20they%20detailed%20their%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20against%20the%20fact-finding%20team%20comes%20after%20three%20people%20%E2%80%93%20a%20leading%20academic%20and%20two%20Kuki%20activists%20%E2%80%93%20%C2%A0were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhyderabad-university-professor-two-kuki-activists-summoned-by-imphal-court-for-interviews-to-the-wire%5C%22%3Esummoned%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20an%20Imphal%20court%20in%20cases%20filed%20by%20Meitei%20activists%20who%20claimed%20that%20statements%20made%20by%20them%20in%20recent%20interviews%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinflamed%20communal%20passions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20women%20had%20said%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20July%202%20that%20the%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20are%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20communal%20violence%20nor%20is%20it%20merely%20a%20fight%20between%20two%20communities.%E2%80%9D%20It%20involves%20the%20%E2%80%9Cquestions%20of%20land%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20fanatics%20and%20militants.%20The%20government%20shrewdly%20carried%20out%20strategies%20to%20materialise%20its%20hidden%20pro-corporate%20agenda%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20the%20current%20crisis%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20violence%E2%80%9D%20which%20%E2%80%9Cdidn%E2%80%99t%20occur%20without%20any%20build-up%E2%80%9D.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fnfiw-team-finds-manipur-violence-sponsored-state%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20clear%20backdrop%20of%20mistrust%20and%20anxiety%20was%20stoked%20amidst%20both%20communities%20by%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20at%20the%20state%20and%20Centre%20to%20precipitate%20a%20full-blown%20civil%20war-like%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20claim%20shows%20that%20the%20women%20are%20conspiring%20%E2%80%9Cto%20overthrow%20a%20democratically%20elected%20government%20by%20instigating%20people%20to%20wage%20war%20against%20the%20Government%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20objecting%20to%20the%20fact-finding%20team%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20the%20violence%20between%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities%20is%20a%20state-sponsored%20violence%2C%20the%20complainant%20has%20also%20taken%20offence%20to%20their%20categorisation%20of%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20his%20resignation%20as%20%E2%80%9Cstage-managed%20drama%E2%80%9D.%20By%20describing%20the%20protests%2C%20which%20Singh%20cited%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20reversing%20his%20decision%2C%20as%20such%2C%20the%20three%20women%20%E2%80%9Cin%20complete%20disregard%20of%20facts%20have%20abused%20the%20woman%20Meira%20Paibis%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Meira%20Paibis%20or%20%E2%80%9Cwomen%20torch%20bearers%E2%80%9D%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-politics%2Fmeira-paibis-manipur-conflict-role-8688898%2F%5C%22%3Eloosely%20organised%20civil%20society%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20march%20through%20the%20streets%20at%20night%20with%20flaming%20torches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20one%20of%20the%20three%20women%2C%20who%20said%20she%20got%20to%20about%20the%20FIR%20through%20various%20local%20media%20reports.%20She%20said%20has%20not%20received%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20yet.%20Asked%20for%20a%20comment%20on%20the%20development%2C%20she%20said%20she%20could%20only%20do%20so%20after%20looking%20at%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnagalandpost.com%2Findex.php%2Fnfiw-terms-manipur-violence-state-sponsored%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ENagaland%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20NFIW%20fact-finding%20team%20said%20on%20July%202%20that%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20as%20as%20the%20elected%20representative%20of%20the%20people%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cresponsible%20for%20protecting%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%20irrespective%20of%20communities%20they%20belonged%20to%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20he%20did%20not%20do%20it.%20He%20fails%20in%20discharging%20his%20constitutional%20responsibility%20of%20protecting%20and%20safeguarding%20life%20and%20livelihood.%20That%20is%20why%20he%20should%20take%20moral%20and%20political%20responsibility%E2%80%A6%20%C2%A0He%20(chief%20minister)%20should%20have%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20within%20the%20week%20after%20violence%20erupted%20on%20May%203%20itself.%20He%20did%20not%20do%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECase%20against%20Kuki%20students%20group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20development%2C%20the%20commisisoner%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20home%20department%20has%20written%20to%20the%20director%20general%20of%20police%2C%20asking%20for%20a%20case%20to%20be%20registered%20against%20the%20Zomi%20Students%E2%80%99%20Federation%20and%20Kuki%20Students%20Organisation%20for%20publishing%20a%20booklet%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20Inevitable%20Split%3A%20Documents%20of%20State-Sponsored%20Ethnic%20Cleansing%20in%20Manipur%2C%202023%E2%80%99%20on%20May%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET.%20Ranjit%20Singh%2C%20commissioner%20(home)%2C%20government%20of%20Manipur%2C%20wrote%20to%20the%20DGP%20on%20July%208%20to%20register%20an%20%E2%80%9CFIR%20and%20take%20stern%20action%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20two%20organisations.%20The%20letter%20references%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20an%20advocate%20Thokchom%20Punshiba%20Singh%20and%20has%20asked%20the%20DGP%20to%20take%20ste