ases.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22http%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarizatioin-countries-central-banks-invesco-survey-gold-assets-repatriation-safekeeping-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Weeks%20After%20It%20Denied%20Rice%20to%20Karnataka%2C%20FCI%20Faces%20Low%20Turnout%20in%20Auction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10124204%2FRice-bags.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20e-auction%20of%20rice%20grains%20held%20by%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%20on%20July%205%20saw%20bids%20for%20only%20170%20tonnes%20out%20of%20the%203.86%20lakh%20tonnes%20of%20grain%20on%20offer%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fno-takers-for-fci-rice-in-e-auction-to-check-inflation-8822060%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FCI%20received%20bids%20for%20rice%20grains%20from%20three%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Karnataka%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20North%20East%20Frontier%20region%2C%20and%20did%20not%20receive%20bids%20from%2016%20other%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERice%20grains%20were%20sold%20in%20the%20auction%20at%20a%20weighted%20average%20price%20of%20Rs%203%2C175.35%20per%20quintal%2C%20against%20the%20country-wide%20reserve%20price%20of%20Rs%203%2C173%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EExpress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FCI%20is%20a%20Union%20government%20agency%20responsible%20for%20the%20procurement%20and%20distribution%20of%20food%20grains.%C