ental%20Pioneer%20of%20Cash%20Transfers%20for%20Food%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20already%20provides%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fkarnataka-rice-row-fci-anna-bhagya-scheme-8688514%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehalf%20the%20required%20amount%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20order%20to%20provide%20the%20remaining%205%20kg%20rice%20per%20BPL%20household%20member%20every%20month%20for%20the%20Anna%20Bhagya%20scheme%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fthe-anna-bhagya-fiasco-and-thinking-beyond-rice%2Farticle67061211.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplanned%20to%20rely%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20FCI%E2%80%99s%20Open%20Market%20Sale%20Scheme%20(OMSS)%2C%20in%20which%20the%20latter%20sells%20procured%20food%20grains%20in%20order%20to%20stabilise%20prices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20a%20day%20after%20the%20FCI%20agreed%20to%20provide%20rice%20for%20Anna%20Bhagya%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20June%2014%20directed%20it%20to%20stop%20selling%20OMSS%20grain%20to%20state%20governments%20(with%20some%20exceptions).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fno-takers-for-fci-rice-in-e-auction-to-check-inflation-8822060%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20although%20the%20FCI%20had%20enough%20grain%20to%20support%20the%20Karnataka%20government%E2%80%99s%20request%2C%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20was%20driven%20by%20concerns%20that%20it%20may%20not%20have%20enough%20grain%20to%20sell%20in%20order%20to%20control%20prices%20if%20other%20states%20make%20similar%20requests%20to%20the%20FCI%20after%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20example.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficials%20also%20told%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EExpress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20monthly%20per-capita%20rice%20consumption%20in%20Karnataka%20stood%20at%205.622%20kg%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%205.213%20kg%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20according%20to%20estimates%20by%20the%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20Office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKarnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20blamed%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20as%20a%20move%20to%20scuttle%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20Anna%20Bhagya%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20is%20always%20anti-Karnataka%20and%20we%20have%20been%20saying%20this%20since%202014%20%E2%80%A6%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20openly%20threatened%20Kannadigas%20during%20elections%20by%20saying%20that%20all%20schemes%20will%20be%20stopped%20if%20BJP%20is%20not%20voted%20to%20power.%20Is%20this%20letter%20to%20FCI%20an%20outcome%20of%20that%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsiddaramaiah%2Fstatus%2F1669235815183187968%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20June%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20since%20then%20decided%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkarnataka-accidental-pioneer-cash-transfers-for-food%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esubstitute%20cash%20for%20rice%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20an%20interim%20arrangement%20in%20the%20Anna%20Bhagya%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688974782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10124204%2FRice-bags.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fafter-cancelling-karnataka-rice-order-fci-sees-few-auction-takers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20e-auction%20the%20Food%20Corporati