2C%20but%20it's%20where%20his%20family%20and%20friends%20like%20to%20hang%20out%20whenever%20they%20come%20for%20a%20visit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Davey%20Pearson%20moved%20into%20his%20new%20home%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20wanted%20a%20space%20where%20he%20could%20get%20away%20from%20his%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20an%20old%20derelict%20garage%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20garden.%20And%20I%20felt%20that's%20an%20ideal%20place%20for%20me%20to%20hide%20away%C2%A0for%20an%20evening%20and%20relax%2C%26quot%3B%20Pearson%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI've%20got%20four%20kids%2C%20so%20you%20can%20imagine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20was%20initially%20meant%20to%20be%20his%20mancave%20ended%20up%20becoming%20somewhere%20his%20family%20could%20spend%20time%20together%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2046-year-old%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22632a34bb95718ff7d30ba159fc04dd6e%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chesworthsestates.co.uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emortgage%20broker%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20living%20in%20Sussex%2C%20a%20county%20in%20the%20south%20of%20England%2C%20but%20relocated%20about%20160%20miles%20north%20to%20Lincolnshire%20due%20to%20rising%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20shed%20in%20his%20backyard%20had%20been%20left%20empty%20by%20the%20previous%20owners%2C%20and%20it%20measured%2018%20feet%20by%209%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20enough%20space%20for%20what%20Pearson%20had%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22978%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20garden%20outside%20of%20the%20shed%20used%20to%20be%20muddy%20and%20unkempt.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a26ea26075be0019c2785f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22733%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20garden%20outside%20of%20the%20shed%20used%20to%20be%20muddy%20and%20unkempt.%3Cp%3EDavey%20Pearson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20it%20wasn't%20his%20first%20time%20turning%20a%20garage%20into%20a%20home%20pub%3B%20he%20had%20done%20something%20similar%20on%20his%20previous%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPearson%20had%20been%20running%20a%20local%20newspaper%20in%20his%20old%20neighborhood%20for%2010%20years%20until%20the%20pandemic%20forced%20him%20to%20shut%20it%20down.%20But%20the%20newspaper%20still%20had%20a%20social%20media%20presence%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20ended%20up%20turning%20his%20old%20garage%20into%20a%20pub%20where%20he%20would%20host%20online%20pub%20quizzes%20that%20were%20streamed%20on%20the%20paper's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheDistrictPostHorsham%2Flive_videos%5C%22%3EFacebook%20page%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20set-up%20back%20then%20included%20a%20simple%20wooden%20tabletop%2C%20a%20beer%20tap%2C%20and%20some%20alcohol%20bottles%20displayed%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20used%20to%20invite%20my%20readers%20to%20join%20me%20on%20a%20Friday%20night%2C%20and%20I%20would%20do%20a%20piece%20to%20camera%20and%20do%20a%20live%20quiz%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Pearson%20noted%20that%20this%20became%20a%20popular%20event%20during%20the%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20moved%20shortly%20after%2C%20and%20it%20was%20those%20positive%20memories%20that%20left%20him%20inspired%20to%20DIY%20another%20one%20in%20his%20new%20home%2C%20Pearson%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20suppose%20I%20quite%20enjoyed%20building%20the%20pub%20that%20I%20had%20in%20my%20previous%20property.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBut%20it%20was%20a%20tall%20task%3A%20The%20shed%20was%20old%2C%20dirty%2C%20and%20lacked%20proper%20flooring.%20It%20didn't%20have%20electricity%20either.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221026%5C%22%20a