l%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'People%20in%20the%20Government%20Were%20Involved%20in%20the%20Attack%20on%20Me'%3A%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10085527%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Bhim%20Army%20chief%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbhim-army-chief-chandra-shekhar-aazad-shot-at-saharanpur%5C%22%3Ewho%20sustained%20a%20bullet%20injury%20after%20his%20convoy%20was%20shot%20at%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20late%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20blamed%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%20the%20state%20for%20the%20attack%20on%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%2028%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbhim-army-chief-chandra-shekhar-aazad-shot-at-saharanpur%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efour%20assailants%20shot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20in%20Saharanpur%E2%80%99s%20Deoband%2C%20where%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20attend%20a%20function%20at%20a%20supporter%E2%80%99s%20house.%20A%20bullet%20grazed%20his%20abdomen.%20He%20was%20in%20his%20car%20when%20the%20attack%20took%20place%2C%20and%20a%20worker%20of%20his%20party%2C%20Manish%2C%20was%20behind%20the%20wheel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Aazad%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20behind%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20the%20Bhim%20Army%20is%20growing%20across%20the%20country%20and%20the%20ideas%20that%20are%20guiding%20the%20Bhim%20Army%20and%20the%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%E2%80%99s%20work%20have%20made%20the%20BJP-RSS%20%5BRashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%5D%20fearful%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aazad%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20attack%20on%20me%20has%20been%20carried%20out%20under%20the%20protection%20of%20those%20in%20power%20because%20when%20you%20are%20not%20able%20to%20stop%20someone%20the%20only%20option%20you%20have%20is%20to%20kill%20them.%20BJP%20has%20understood%20that%20it%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20stop%20the%20Bhim%20Army%20and%20the%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party.%20%E2%80%98That%20is%20why%20their%20leader%20should%20be%20killed%20so%20that%20others%20too%20get%20scared%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20thought%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fharyana-taxi-driver-4-held-firing-bhim-army-chief-chandra-shekhar-aazad-8697494%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20four%20young%20men%20were%20arrested%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20after%20a%20joint%20operation%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Special%20Task%20Force%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20said%20that%20of%20the%20four%2C%20three%20have%20a%20criminal%20record%20including%20charges%20of%20attempted%20murder%2C%20assault%20and%20intimidation%2C%20and%20were%20out%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20have%20admitted%20that%20three%20of%20the%20accused%20have%20criminal%20cases.%20Those%20whose%20work%20is%20to%20kill%20people%20cannot%20be%20the%20custodians%20of%20any%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aazad%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20with%20previous%20criminal%20charges%20are%20all%20residents%20of%20Rankhandi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Saharanpur%20district.%20They%20are%20Vikas%20alias%20Vicky%2C%20Prashant%20and%20Lavish%20alias%20Abhishek.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fourth%20accused%2C%20also%20named%20Vikas%2C%20is%20a%20taxi%20driver%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Karnal%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20are%20members%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20Rajput%20community.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EThey%20told%20police%20that%20they%20attacked%20the%20Dalit%20leader%20as%20they%20were%20upset%20by%20his%20statements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EVIDEO%20%7C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20arrested%20four%20persons%20%E2%80%93%20Vicky%20from%20Haryana%2C%20another%20Vicky%20from%20Rankhandi%2C%20Prashant%20and%20Lavish%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Haryana.%20They%20carried%20out%20the%20attack%20because%20they%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20some%20of%20the%20remarks%20of%20Chandrashekhar%20Azad%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Saharanpur%20Police%20on%20attack%20on%20Bhim%20Army%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2k5HTKUyac%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2k5HTKUyac%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1675410540871528448%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20political%20conspiracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20said%20last%20week%20that%20they%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fattack-on-bhim-army-chief-arrested-youths-were-unhappy-with-aazads-remarks-up-police-8697821%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseized%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20two%20country-made%20pistols%2C%20cartridges%20and%20a%20car%20allegedly%20used%20in%20the%20crime%20based%20on%20the%20information%20provided%20by%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20did%20they%20get%20weapons%3F%20Who%20gave%20them%20these%20weapons%3F%20Police%20have%20to%20answer%20these%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aazad%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20planning%20but%20that%20they%20suddenly%20found%20out%20about%20my%20convoy%20and%20decided%20to%20fire%20on%20me.%20This%20is%20an%20almost%20laughable%20statement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20statements%20show%20that%20they%20are%20protecting%20people%20in%20high%20places%20and%20that%20the%20mastermind%20of%20this%20incident%20is%20being%20protected.%20This%20was%20a%20political%20conspiracy%20and%20people%20in%20the%20government%20are%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Aazad%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20him%20shows%20that%20the%20Adityanath%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20UP%20improving%20are%20hollow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20provided%20their%20%5Bthe%20accused%20persons%E2%80%99%5D%20identity%20to%20the%20police.%20We%20told%20the%20police%20about%20their%20car%20number%20and%20that%20they%20had%20automatic%20weapons.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20shows%20intelligence%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20police%20that%20people%20who%20possess%20weapons%20are%20roaming%20freely%20and%20the%20police%20know%20nothing%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aazad%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20person%20like%20me%20can%20be%20attacked%20then%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20common%20man%3F%20How%20can%20the%20common%20man%20be%20safe%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAazad%20said%20that%20he%20was%20attacked%20because%20the%20BJP%20government%20knows%20that%20he%20is%20not%20scared%20of%20being%20jailed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20government%20knows%20that%20they%20cannot%20scare%20me%20with%20the%20CBI-ED%20%5BCentral%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation-Enforcement%20Directorate%5D%20cases%20or%20by%20putting%20me%20in%20jail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Mahatma%20Gandhi%20or%20Phoolan%20Devi%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20July%20Aazad%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjaipur-magistrate-orders-bhim-army-chief-chandra-shekhar-azads-release%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earrested%20and%20spent%20two%20days%20in%20judicial%20custody%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Jaipur%20after%20reaching%20the%20city%20to%20join%3C%2Fspan%3E%20a%20protest%20by%20COVID%20Health%20Assistants%2C%20demanding%20permanent%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20said%20that%20his%20%E2%80%9Cpreventive%E2%80%9D%20arrest%20was%20made%20as%20Section%20144%20was%20in%20force%20after%20tailor%20Kanhaiya%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20murder%20in%20Udaipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%202019%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchandra-shekhar-aazad-ravan-bail-caa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20arrested%20and%20jailed%20for%20a%20month%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20he%20led%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20September%202018%20he%20was%20released%20after%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbhim-army-chief-chandrashekhar-azad-release-up-govt%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%2015%20months%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20been%20booked%20under%20the%20NSA%20for%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20violence%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Shabbirpur%2C%20a%20village%20in%20Saharanpur%20district%2C%20in%20May%202017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20the%20only%20person%20to%20be%20targeted%20like%20this%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20or%20Phoolan%20Devi%20whoever%20speaks%20up%20about%20injustices%20is%20killed.%20Without%20the%20cooperation%20of%20those%20in%20power%20such%20an%20attack%20is%20not%20possible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Aazad%20is%20recovering%20from%20his%20injury%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20attack%20has%20not%20made%20him%20fearful%20in%20any%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20question%20of%20fear%2C%20yes%20but%20I%20have%20become%20more%20cautious.%20NCRB%20%5BNational%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%5D%20data%20shows%20that%20every%2030%20minutes%20a%20woman%20is%20raped%20or%20killed%20in%20our%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20life%20is%20not%20important%2C%20but%20it%20is%20important%20to%20highlight%20the%20injustices%20that%20lower%20castes%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20face%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20given%20a%20second%20life%20with%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20previous%20life%20was%20also%20dedicated%20to%20the%20deprived%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20this%20life%20too%20will%20be%20dedicated%20to%20their%20upliftment%20and%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Lower%20castes%20never%20considered%20humans%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20atrocities%20against%20people%20from%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20communities%20that%20have%20made%20national%20headlines%2C%20Aazad%20said%20that%20such%20attacks%20have%20continued%20because%20the%20people%20and%20parties%20who%20have%20held%20positions%20of%20power%20%E2%80%9Chave%20never%20considered%20the%20lower%20castes%20as%20human%20beings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20week%20a%20video%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%20in%20which%20a%20man%20identified%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmp-urination-incident-victims-wife-worried-about-husbands-whereabouts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPravesh%20Shukla%2C%20allegedly%20a%20BJP%20worker%2C%20was%20seen%20urinating%20on%20the%20face%20of%20an%20Adivasi%20worke%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Er.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20outrage%2C%20Shukla%20was%20arrested%20and%20his%20house%20was%20demolished%20to%20send%20out%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20message%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20visited%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20washed%20his%20feet%20in%20front%20of%20cameras.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Sonbhadra%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Futtar-pradesh-dalit-man-assaulted-forced-to-lick-mans-shoes-accused-arrested%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDalit%20man%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20and%20forced%20to%20lick%20the%20shoes%20of%20a%20contractual%20power%20worker%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20the%20two%20incidents%20Aazad%20said%20that%20they%20show%20a%20clear%20trend.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20elections%20are%20coming%20in%20MP%20they%20%5BBJP%5D%20will%20wash%20their%20feet%2C%20they%20will%20eat%20with%20them.%20But%20since%20UP%20elections%20are%20not%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20does%20not%20care%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20injustices%20will%20end%20only%20when%20the%20deprived%20sections%20of%20society%20will%20become%20aware%20and%20will%20have%20political%20power.%20Even%20now%20the%20fact%20they%20are%20not%20considered%20as%20human%20beings%20is%20because%20those%20who%20have%20been%20in%20political%20parties%20and%20held%20power%2C%20they%20have%20not%20considered%20them%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20incidents%20will%20not%20stop%20till%20these%20deprived%20sections%20take%20hold%20of%20political%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAazad%20said%20that%20his%20political%20outfit%2C%20the%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20which%20he%20founded%20in%202020%2C%20will%20contest%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20on%20the%20plank%20of%20uplifting%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20deprived%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20conducting%20rallies%2C%20strengthening%20our%20booth%20level%20organisation%2C%20raising%20awareness%20around%20SC-ST%20%5BScheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%5D%20communities%20and%20making%20a%20list%20of%20possible%20candidates.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20believe%20that%20in%20these%20elections%20people%20will%20vote%20not%20for%20those%20who%20have%20money%20power%20but%20those%20who%20are%20doing%20work.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Alliance%20only%20if%20we%20align%20on%20issues%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Azaad%2C%20while%20opposition%20parties%20are%20holding%20meetings%20to%20put%20up%20what%20could%20possible%20be%20a%20joint%20fight%20against%20BJP%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20alliances%20can%20only%20be%20worked%20out%20if%20they%20align%20on%20issues%20of%20ending%20caste-based%20injustices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpatna-amidst-aap-congress-sparring-16-opposition-parties-vow-to-unitedly-fight-the-bjp%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E16%20opposition%20parties%20met%20in%20Patna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20decide%20on%20a%20joint%20opposition%20front%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-second-opposition-meet-delhi-ordinance-issue-still-divides-aap-and-congress%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esecond%20meeting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20finalise%20plans%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Bengaluru%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20any%20of%20these%20opposition%20parties%2C%20Azaad%20said%20that%20a%20decision%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20taken%20by%20his%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20opposition%20alliance%20will%20be%20decided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20ideologies%20and%20principles.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20core%20committee%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20and%20this%20will%20be%20communicated%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attack%20on%20Azad%20has%20been%20condemned%20by%20various%20political%20parties%20including%20by%20leaders%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESamajwadi%20Party%2C%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20agenda%20is%20clear%2C%20that%20is%20to%20highlight%20caste%20based%20violence%20especially%20especially%20against%20women%2C%20ensure%20promotions%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20reservations%2C%20clear%20the%20backlog%20in%20reserved%20posts%20in%20government%20appointments%20for%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBCs.%20These%20are%20our%20main%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20align%20on%20these%20issues%20only%20then%20can%20we%20build%20an%20alliance.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20parties%20know%20change%20cannot%20be%20brought%20without%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20so%20for%20any%20opposition%20alliance%20to%20be%20successful%20they%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%