3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmit%20Naik%20from%20Ausgram%20in%20East%20Burdwan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20vote%2C%20armed%20goons%20are%20watching%20over.%20They%20will%20not%20allow%20us%20to%20vote.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20file%20a%20complaint%20anywhere.%20Even%20if%20the%20commission%20picks%20up%20the%20phone%2C%20they%20are%20not%20giving%20any%20assurance.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20remote%20villages%20in%20East%20Medinipur%20to%20posh%20localities%20in%20New%20town%2C%20many%20people%20like%20Amit%20could%20not%20vote.%20But%20their%20votes%20were%20cast.%20The%20deployment%20of%20approximately%20660%20companies%20of%20central%20forces%20was%20much%20less%20than%20allotted%20822%20companies%20making%20the%20lack%20of%20security%20in%20and%20around%20the%20polling%20booths%20evident.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPratima%20Mandal%20of%20Khejuri%20Ramchak%20in%20East%20Medinipur%20tried%20to%20contact%20the%20commission%20all%20day%20without%20success.%20Her%20husband%20and%20son%20were%20allegedly%20knocked%20unconscious%20by%20supporters%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC).%20Till%20late%20evening%20on%20Saturday%2C%20she%20did%20not%20get%20any%20medical%20or%20security%20help.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20New%20Town%2C%20the%20satellite%20township%20bordering%20Kolkata%2C%20residents%20living%20in%20high-rises%20and%20gated%20communities%20have%20reported%20incidents%20of%20intimidation%2C%20threats%2C%20and%20being%20prevented%20from%20casting%20their%20votes%20by%20unknown%20individuals%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20%E2%80%98vote%20boycott%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Mayusehwar%2C%20Birbhum%2C%20the%20presiding%20officer%20Rangana%20Sen%20was%20in%20tears%20while%20miscreants%20were%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20fraudulent%20voting.%20Rampant%20rigging%20took%20place%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20law%20enforcement%20and%20presiding%20officers.%20In%20Dinhata%2C%20Cooch%20Behar%20district%2C%20a%20presiding%20officer%20reported%20that%20miscreants%20had%20forcibly%20entered%20the%20polling%20station%2C%20held%20him%20at%20gunpoint%2C%20and%20stamped%20the%20symbol%20of%20a%20particular%20political%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20unlike%20the%20past%20few%20Panchayat%20elections%2C%20a%20notable%20aspect%20of%20the%20day%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cresistance%E2%80%9D%20shown%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties.%20In%20Kanksa%2C%20the%20tribals%20valiantly%20resisted%20the%20attack.%20In%20the%20remote%20villages%20of%20Basanti%20in%20South%2024%20Parganas%2C%20a%20few%20women%20used%20social%20media%20to%20inform%20people%20about%20booth%20capturing%20and%20violence%20which%20went%20viral.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20another%20part%20of%20the%20district%2C%20a%20villager%20saw%20false%20voting%20happening%20even%20before%20the%20polling%20began%20and%20threw%20the%20ballot%20box%20open.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20violence%20prone%20Murshidabad%E2%80%99s%20Bharatpur%20and%20Salar%20areas%2C%20a%20section%20of%20TMC%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20opposition%20parties%20to%20resist%20booth%20capturing.%20Across%20the%20state%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20found%20themselves%20under%20attack%20from%20opposition%20parties.%20Majority%20of%20those%20party%20workers%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20on%20Saturday%20were%20known%20to%20be%20TMC%20supporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Purulia%2C%20at%20Booth%20No.%20106%20in%20Poonacha%2C%20the%20outgoing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Zilla%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Parishad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Sabhapati%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESujoy%20Banerjee%20had%20to%20be%20rescued%20by%20the%20police%20after%20angry%20villagers%20surrounded%20him%20for%20allegedly%20tampering%20with%20the%20voting%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Kultali%2C%20South%2024%20Parganas%2C%20a%20clash%20erupted%20between%20the%20booth%20encroachers%20and%20villagers%2C%20resulting%20in%20one%20death.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20Swarupnagar%2C%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20the%20villagers%20retaliated%20by%20seizing%20motorcycles%20from%20the%20assailants%20and%20throwing%20them%20into%20a%20nearby%20pond.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20TMC%20is%20trying%20to%20deflect%20allegations%20of%20violence%20citing%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20side.%20According%20to%20an%20exit%20poll%20survey%20by%20C-Voter%20for%20local%20ABP%20Ananda%20channel%2C%20TMC%20is%20expected%20to%20retain%20most%20of%20the%20districts.%20Political%20experts%20in%20West%20Bengal%20are%20also%20keeping%20them%20ahead%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Left-Congress%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20panchayat%20election%20in%20Bengal%20that%20displayed%20a%20comparable%20pattern%20was%20the%20one%20in%202008%20when%20the%20ruling%20Left%20Front%20faced%20a%20similar%20%E2%80%9Cresistance%E2%80%9D%20from%20a%20rising%20TMC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20much%20of%20the%20resistance%20coming%20from%20areas%20with%20sizable%20minority%20populations%20and%20the%20visuals%20of%20violence%2C%20dead%20bodies%20and%20electoral%20rigging%20likely%20to%20dent%20its%20image%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20Bengal%20has%20valid%20concerns%20about%20the%20long-term%20repercussions%20of%20the%20events%20that%20transpired%20in%20the%20past%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688957109000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09174943%2FF0k2Jm8WwAMCWIo.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2F18-deaths-voters-who-couldnt-vote-violence-during-w