20the%20tall%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20government%20and%20local%20bodies%2C%20even%20metropolitan%20cities%20witnessed%20extreme%20waterlogging%20and%20traffic%20snarls%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days.%20As%20Delhi%20witnessed%20almost%20incessant%20rainfall%20for%20two%20days%2C%20roads%20across%20the%20city%20were%20waterlogged%2C%20including%20the%20one%20leading%20to%20the%20capital's%20PWD%20Minister%20Atishi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20Gautam%2C%20who%20works%20in%20Delhi's%20Nehru%20Place%2C%20told%20NDTV%20his%20bike%20stopped%20after%20being%20submerged%20in%20knee-deep%20water%20in%20South%20Delhi's%20Pamposh%20Enclave.%20It%20took%20him%20more%20than%20four%20hours%20to%20get%20back%20home%20as%20his%20bike%20stopped%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20resident%2C%20Arun%2C%20said%20he%20fell%20into%20a%20deep%20puddle%20in%20East%20Delhi's%20Shahdara.%20Arun%20added%20that%20people%20in%20Shahdara%20have%20not%20even%20been%20able%20to%20go%20to%20work%20because%20of%20inundated%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYear%20after%20year%2C%20the%20national%20capital%20witnesses%20intense%20waterlogging%20during%20the%20monsoons.%20Until%20last%20year%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20the%20centre%20blamed%20the%20MCD%20for%20collapsing%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20city%20as%20the%20BJP%20ruled%20the%20local%20body.%20But%20according%20to%20the%20residents%2C%20the%20waterlogging%20situation%20has%20gotten%20worse%20after%20the%20AAP%20government%20took%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20Gaur%2C%20a%20Delhi%20resident%2C%20said%20he%20was%20stuck%20on%20a%20waterlogged%20road%20and%20couldn't%20visit%20his%20mother-in-law%20who%20recently%20underwent%20a%20surgery.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20NDTV%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20route%20from%20North%20Delhi's%20Ashok%20Vihar%20to%20Burari%2C%20that%20usually%20takes%20him%20around%2015%20minutes%2C%20took%20him%20two%20hours%20today.%20Even%20after%20making%20it%20thro