y%20Project%2C%20Sharma%20said%20in%20his%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20their%20investigation%20found%20that%20the%20email%20address%20rajeev.osd.mha%40gmail.com%20was%20fake%20and%20created%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20deceiving%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20technical%20surveillance%2C%20our%20team%20zeroed%20in%20on%20the%20prime%20suspect%20Robin%20Upadhyay%20and%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20technical%20analysis%2C%20it%20was%20learned%20that%20the%20mail%20was%20created%20six-seven%20days%20ago%20and%20was%20found%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Upadhyay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20suspect%20was%20subsequently%20traced%20and%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20initial%20interrogation%2C%20he%20was%20detained%20from%20his%20home%20in%20Meerut%20on%20Saturday%20evening%20and%20later%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Hemant%20Tiwari%2C%20Additional%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(New%20Delhi)%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20interrogated%2C%20Upadhyay%20revealed%20that%20being%20a%20civil%20engineer%2C%20he%20had%20a%20vast%20experience%20in%20civil%20construction%20projects%2C%20and%20he%20thought%20of%20securing%20a%20fake%20reference%20to%20get%20a%20job%2C%20Tiwari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHence%2C%20he%20searched%20about%20ongoing%20highway%20projects%20and%20their%20progress.%20After%20that%2C%20he%20created%20an%20email%20id%20impersonating%20Rajeev%20Kumar%2C%20OSD%20to%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20also%20attached%20his%20CV%20showing%20his%20credentials%20to%20get%20the%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Tiwari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688928540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Fugua930g_delhi-police-generic_625