ed%20as%20the%20protests%20turned%20violent%20in%20the%20Chakulia%20police%20station%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20workers%20held%20similar%20protests%20in%20Murshidabad%20district's%20Beldanga%2C%20alleging%20that%20supporters%20of%20the%20ruling%20TMC%20indulged%20in%20intimidation%20of%20voters%20and%20false%20voting%20with%20impunity%20during%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20was%20also%20reported%20from%20the%20district's%20Samserganj%20area%20where%20two%20groups%20clashed%20with%20crude%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Amdanga%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20clashes%20boke%20out%20between%20ISF%20and%20TMC%20supporters.%20Crude%20bombs%20were%20hurled%20during%20the%20clashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20South%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20three%20police%20personnel%20were%20injured%20while%20trying%20to%20control%20a%20clash%20between%20TMC%20and%20Congress%20supporters.%20The%20incident%20happened%20in%20Nainan%20in%20Magrahat%20police%20station%20area%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClashes%20were%20also%20reported%20from%20the%20district's%20Kulpi%20area%20as%20supporters%20of%20an%20Independent%20candidate%20and%20TMC%20workers%20clashed%20in%20Udairampur%20village.%20Later%20when%20police%20reached%20the%20area%2C%20women%20protested%20with%20sticks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688921700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fvbmond04_bengal-poll-security-pti_625x300_09_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepolling-tomorrow-at-several-booths-after-bengal-panchayat-polls-hit-by-violence-4191998%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20West%20Bengal%20State%20Election%20Commission%20announced%20that%20repolling%20will%20be%20held%20on%20Monday%20in%20all%20booths%20where%20voting%2