roversial-stumping-player-is-run-out-for-leaving-crease-to-congratulate-fellow-batter-watch-4191622%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20player%20tried%20to%20get%20back%20to%20his%20end%2C%20it%20was%20too%20little%20too%20late%20as%20the%20keeper%20took%20of%20the%20bails%20in%20a%20flash.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22http%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A526%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fashes-2023%2Fafter-jonny-bairstows-controversial-stumping-player-is-run-out-for-leaving-crease-to-congratulate-fellow-batter-watch-4191622%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fashes-2023%2Fafter-jonny-bairstows-controversial-stumping-player-is-run-out-for-leaving-crease-to-congratulate-fellow-batter-watch-4191622%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fashes-2023%2Fafter-jonny-bairstows-controversial-stumping-player-is-run-out-for-leaving-crease-to-congratulate-fellow-batter-watch-4191622%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition%20Must%20Not%20Let%20Small%20Differences%20Come%20in%20the%20Way%20of%20the%20Battle%20to%20Save%20Democracy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09144815%2FAAP-Congress.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2012%20years%20he%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20nine%20in%20which%20he%20has%20been%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20shown%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20that%20he%20is%20built%20somewhat%20like%20a%20powerful%20automobile%20in%20which%20the%20manufacturers%20forgot%20to%20put%20in%20a%20reverse%20gear.%20Because%20throughout%20these%20years%2C%20his%20only%20response%20to%20every%20threat%20he%20has%20faced%20has%20been%20to%20launch%20a%20counter-attack%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20it%20might%20cost%20the%20nation%20or%20even%20his%20own%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20therefore%20been%20waiting%20for%20his%20counterattack%20to%20take%20shape%20ever%20since%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20forming%20a%20combined%20front%20to%20fight%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%202024%2C%20at%20Patna.%20I%20got%20my%20answer%20on%20July%205.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20had%20been%20the%20convenor%20who%20had%20made%20the%20Patna%20meet%20possible.%20So%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20party%20had%20to%20be%20destroyed%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weapon%20that%20Modi%20has%20used%20is%20the%20one%20he%20has%20been%20using%20with%20increasing%20frequency%20against%20his%20political%20opponents%20and%20critics%20in%20civil%20society.%20This%20is%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20in%20which%20he%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fcolumns%2Famendments-to-pmla-by-finance-act-2019-widening-the-scope-of-the-legislation%5C%22%3Eeight%20draconian%20amendments%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%20that%20have%20given%20his%20government%20virtually%20unrestricted%20powers%20of%20arrest%2C%20detention%20and%20attachment%20of%20property%2C%20and%20all%20but%20abolished%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehabeas%20corpus%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20right%20of%20the%20accused%20to%20remain%20free%20until%20convicted%20of%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Modi%20has%20been%20relying%20more%20and%20more%20heavily%20upon%20the%20PMLA%20to%20%E2%80%98persuade%E2%80%99%20his%20political%20opponents%20to%20betray%20their%20parties%20and%20join%20the%20BJP.%20His%20destruction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20has%20run%20true%20to%20form%3A%20four%20of%20the%20nine%20defectors%20%E2%80%93%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20Praful%20Patel%2C%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20and%20Hasan%20Mushrif%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20under%20investigation%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20money%20laundering%20and%20bank%20loan%20scam%20charges%2C%20and%20have%20had%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20worth%20of%20their%20properties%20sequestered.%20Now%20that%20they%20have%20become%20honourable%20ministers%20of%20the%20government%20and%20ruling%20party%20of%20the%20great%20state%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20one%20can%20presume%20that%20these%20charges%20will%20disappear%20like%20the%20mists%20of%20the%20night%20at%20the%20rising%20of%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20this%20has%20been%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20revenge%20on%20Pawar%20has%20been%20endorsed%20by%20no%20less%20eminent%20a%20journal%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fnews-analysis%2Fstory%2Fajit-pawar-ncp-crisis-sharad-pawar-maharashtra-bihar-opposition-nitish-kumar-2024-polls-2401108-2023-07-03%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20also%20warned%20that%20Bihar%20is%20next%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20list.%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20surmised%20that%20this%20is%20only%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20campaign%20that%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20other%20opposition-ruled%20states%20as%20well.%20Its%20purpose%2C%20the%20weekly%20has%20surmised%2C%20is%20to%20show%20to%20the%20people%20how%20unworthy%20of%20trust%20their%20representatives%20are%20and%20to%20remind%20them%20that%20only%20a%20party%20with%20a%20clearly%20stated%20ideology%20can%20be%20relied%20upon%20to%20fulfil%20its%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20Rebellion%20and%20What%20It%20Means%20for%20Opposition%20Unity%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fajit-pawar-rebellion-opposition-unity%5C%22%3EAjit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20Rebellion%20and%20What%20It%20Means%20for%20Opposition%20Unity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20challenge%20that%20the%20opposition%20now%20needs%20to%20meet.%20With%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20less%20than%20nine%20months%20away%2C%20its%20first%20task%20must%20be%20to%20reassure%20the%20electorate%20that%20the%20unity%20achieved%20at%20Patna%20remains%20undented%20by%20the%20developments%20in%20Maharashtra.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20it%20needs%20first%20to%20highlight%20the%20progress%20it%20has%20made%20in%20removing%20the%20obstacles%20that%20have%20hindered%20the%20move%20from%20competition%20to%20cooperation.%20To%20say%20that%20this%20has%20been%20impressive%20would%20be%20an%20understatement%2C%20for%20the%20conclave%20reached%20an%20agreement%20not%20only%20on%20the%20yardsticks%20it%20would%20use%20to%20decide%20which%20party%20would%20contest%20which%20constituency%2C%20but%20agreed%20to%20leave%20the%20even%20more%20thorny%20issue%20of%20leadership%20to%20be%20decided%20after%20the%20elections.%20It%20also%20recognised%20the%20need%20to%20present%20an%20alternative%20vision%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20future%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20impressive%20achievements%2C%20doubts%20about%20the%20stability%20and%20longevity%20of%20the%20coalition%20have%20continued%20to%20persist.%20These%20have%20been%20fuelled%20to%20some%20degree%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Odisha%2C%20and%20of%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20leader%20Mayawati%2C%20but%20their%20main%20cause%20is%20the%20explicit%20refusal%20of%20the%20Aam%20Admi%20Party%20to%20endorse%20the%20Common%20Declaration%20because%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-second-opposition-meet-delhi-ordinance-issue-still-divides-aap-and-congress%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20include%20a%20commitment%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20Delhi%20ordinance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Kejriwal%20need%20not%20have%20insisted%20upon%20this%2C%20because%20the%20ordinance%20is%20outrageous%20anyway%2C%20and%20would%20hamstring%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20too%2C%20were%20they%20ever%20to%20come%20to%20power%20in%20Delhi.%20What%20is%20more%2C%20it%20was%20openly%20mischievous%20for%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20lost%20this%20battle%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20once%20already%20and%20was%20bound%20to%20do%20so%20again.%20Its%20sole%20purpose%2C%20therefore%2C%20was%20to%20give%20the%20simmering%20hatred%20of%20the%20AAP%20within%20the%20Delhi%20branch%20of%20the%20Congress%20an%20occasion%20to%20surface%20and%20thereby%20throw%20a%20spanner%20in%20the%20works%20of%20creating%20a%20unified%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20recognise%20this%2C%20and%20readily%20concede%20to%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20demand%2C%20was%20therefore%20a%20chink%20in%20opposition%20unity%20that%20virtually%20invited%20exploitation%20by%20the%20BJP.%20That%20is%20the%20chink%20that%20it%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20widen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20hard%20to%20understand%20is%20why%20this%20simple%20request%20has%20proved%20an%20obstacle%20to%20unity%20when%20much%20more%20serious%20obstacles%20have%20already%20been%20overcome.%20The%20only%20explanation%20is%20the%20impact%20that%20a%20concession%20by%20either%20party%20would%20have%20had%20upon%20its%20own%20party%20cadres.%20Despite%20the%20cementing%20and%20revitalising%20impact%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20has%20had%20upon%20the%20Congress%2C%20its%20unity%20remains%20fragile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20including%2C%20notably%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bengal%2C%20its%20repeated%20defeats%20at%20the%20hustings%20have%20made%20it%20virtually%20cease%20to%20exist.%20It%20cannot%20therefore%20be%20blamed%20for%20fearing%20that%20after%20suffering%20three%20successive%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20poll%20defeats%2C%20its%20cadres%20in%20Delhi%20are%20also%20headed%20out%20of%20the%20door.%20Ajay%20Maken%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20attacks%20upon%20AAP%20are%20therefore%20attempts%20to%20stem%20the%20rot%2C%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20cannot%20be%20blamed%20for%20not%20reigning%20him%20in%2C%20because%20of%20the%20effect%20this%20could%20have%20upon%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20cadres%20in%20other%20states%20where%20its%20dominance%20is%20endangered%20or%20has%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Modi%20May%20Dismiss%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20Efforts%20To%20Unite%2C%20but%20They%20Are%20Borne%20Out%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hegemony%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-dismiss-oppositions-unity-bjp-hegemony%5C%22%3EModi%20May%20Dismiss%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20Efforts%20To%20Unite%2C%20but%20They%20Are%20Borne%20Out%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hegemony%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Maken%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20attacks%20upon%20the%20AAP%20have%20created%20a%20mirror%20image%20of%20the%20problem%20he%20faces%20within%20the%20Congress%20for%20Kejriwal%20within%20his%20own%20party.%20For%20through%20its%20silent%20endorsement%20of%20every%20attack%20that%20Modi%20has%20launched%20upon%20Kejriwal%20since%202015%2C%20Maken%20had%20made%20it%20virtually%20impossible%20for%20Kejriwal%20to%20join%20the%20opposition%20without%20some%20overt%20act%20of%20support%20for%20AAP%20in%20its%20constant%20battle%20with%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20important%20is%20for%20the%20opposition%20to%20convey%20to%20the%20public%20that%20in%20the%20battle%20to%20defeat%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20in%202024%2C%20the%20differences%20between%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20signify%20nothing.%20AAP%20does%20not%20need%20the%20support%20of%20the%20coalition%20to%20rout%20BJP%20in%20either%20of%20the%20two%20states%20that%20it%20now%20governs.%20In%20Delhi%20it%20won%2067%20and%2062%20out%20of%20the%2070%20vidhan%20Sabha%20seats%20with%20a%20colossal%2054%25%20of%20the%20vote%20in%202015%20and%2053.6%25%20in%202020.%20These%20are%20figures%20that%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20even%20come%20close%20to%20matching%20either%20at%20the%20Centre%20or%20in%20any%20of%20the%20states%20from%201947%20till%201989.%20In%20Punjab%2C%20AAP%20won%2092%20out%20of%20117%20seats%20last%20year%20with%2042%25%20of%20the%20vote.%20Against%20this%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20and%20Akali%20Dal%20together%20won%20only%2023%20seats%20with%2023.9%25%2C%206.6%25%20and%2018%25%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20these%20results%20send%20is%20unambiguous%3A%20whether%20the%20AAP%20joins%20or%20does%20not%20join%20the%20coalition%20formally%20in%202024%20will%20make%20no%20difference%20to%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20it%20will%20win%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20is%20there%20the%20faintest%20chance%20that%20AAP%20will%20enter%20into%20any%20post-poll%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20for%20not%20only%20has%20it%20suffered%20more%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20hands%20than%20any%20other%20party%2C%20but%20it%20would%20destroy%20every%20tenet%20upon%20which%20its%20meteoric%20rise%20has%20been%20based.%20These%20are%20its%20complete%20disregard%20for%20caste%2C%20creed%2C%20colour%20and%20gender%20in%20its%20policies%20and%20governance%2C%20and%20its%20commitment%20to%20serving%20the%20poor%20instead%20of%20being%20served%20by%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20AAP%20will%20contribute%20more%20to%20the%20saving%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20by%20refusing%20to%20compromise%20on%20its%20demand%20for%20support%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20being%20willing%20to%20fight%20alone%20if%20necessary%2C%20than%20by%20making%20any%20of%20the%20compromises%20that%20will%20be%20necessary%20to%20become%20part%C2%A0%20of%20an%20alliance%20of%20political%20parties.%20For%20it%20will%20demonstrate%20to%20the%20entire%20nation%20that%20the%20era%20of%20entitlement%20politics%2C%20in%20which%20candidates%20demanded%20votes%20from%20the%20electorate%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20caste%20or%20creed%2C%20has%20ended%20and%20that%20of%20service%20politics%2C%20in%20which%20votes%20have%20to%20be%20won%20by%20serving%20the%20people%2C%20has%20finally%20dawned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprem-shankar-jha%5C%22%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688910519000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09144815%2FAAP-Congress.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fopposition-must-not-let-small-differences-come-in-the-way-of-the-battle-to-save-democracy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20is%20important%20is%20for%20the%20opposition%20to%20convey%20to%20the%20public%20that%20in%20the%20battle%20to%20defeat%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20in%202024%2C%20the%20differences%20between%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20signify%20nothing.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22https%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fopposition-must-not-let-small-differences-come-in-the-way-of-the-battle-to-save-democracy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20Despite%20Silence%20From%20the%20State%2C%20Families%20of%20Missing%20Persons%20Continue%20to%20Protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154245%2Fprotesters3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarachi%20(Pakistan)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Families%20of%20Baloch%20and%20Sindhi%20missing%20persons%20in%20different%20Pakistani%20cities%20held%20protests%20on%20Eid-al%20Adha%2C%20June%2028%2C%20against%20enforced%20disappearances.%20In%20Karachi%2C%20Dr%20Deen%20Muhammad%20Baloch%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20other%20Baloch%20families%20led%20a%20march%20from%20the%20Art%20Council%20to%20Karachi%20Press%20Club%2C%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20all%20missing%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBaba%20zindagi%20bohate%20kathin%20hoti%20ja%20rahi%20hai%2C%20ek%20ek%20lamha%20sadiyon%20jesa%20mehsoos%20hota%20hai%E2%80%A6%20Mujhe%20ek%20nakaam%20aur%20bebas%20aur%20bad-bakhat%20qarar%20deti%20hai%2C%20kaise%20is%20haqeeqat%20ke%20saath%20mein%20aur%20zindagi%20guzarun%2C%20jis%20din%20in%20lavaahiqin%20ka%20bharosa%20insaaf%20se%20uth%20gaya%2C%20tu%20apni%20adalat%20khud%20qaim%20karen%20gaye%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Father%2C%20life%20has%20becomes%20challenging%2C%20each%20moment%20is%20unbearable%20and%20feels%20like%20a%20century.%20It%20makes%20me%20helpless%20%E2%80%93%20how%20long%20will%20I%20continue%20to%20live%20with%20such%20a%20bitter%20truth%3F%20The%20day%20when%20the%20kin%20of%20missing%20persons%20will%20no%20longer%20hope%20for%20justice%2C%20we%2C%20on%20that%20day%2C%20will%20hold%20our%20own%20court)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mehlab%20Deen%20Baloch%2C%20her%20voice%20full%20of%20anguish%2C%20at%20the%20Karachi%20Press%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Deen%20Muhammad%20Baloch%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20security%20agencies%20from%20Khuzdar%2C%20Balochistan%20on%20June%2028%2C%202009.%20He%20was%20performing%20his%20duties%20in%20a%20hospital%20when%20security%20agencies%20allegedly%20abducted%20him.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family%20has%20been%20demanding%20his%20return%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehlab%20was%20eight%20years%20old%20when%20she%20got%20to%20know%20that%20her%20father%20had%20disappeared.%20Now%2C%20she%20is%2025%2C%20and%20her%20life%20has%20been%20a%20continuous%20protest.%20She%20had%20spent%20numerous%20months%20at%20protest%20camps%20for%20missing%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20not%20peculiar%20to%20Mehlab.%20It%20is%20true%20for%20every%20victim%2C%20regardless%20of%20what%20ethnicity%20they%20belong%20to%20%E2%80%93%20Baloch%2C%20Sindhi%20or%20Pashtun.%20These%20days%20abduction%20is%20not%20as%20common%20in%20Pakistan%3B%20there%20was%20a%20time%2C%20however%2C%20when%20it%20was%20the%20state%20agencies%E2%80%99%20chosen%20method%20to%20silence%20dissent.%20Former%20president%20General%20Pervez%20Musharraf%2C%20who%20took%20power%20through%20a%20coup%2C%20adopted%20abduction%20as%20an%20unstated%20policy.%20Ever%20since%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20military%20establishment%20has%20allegedly%20abducted%20innumerable%20people.%20Now%20people%20make%20jokes%20about%20it%20%E2%80%93%20if%20you%20say%20something%20the%20establishment%20won%E2%80%99t%20like%2C%20a%20Vigo%20car%20will%20pop%20up%20and%20pick%20you%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20an%20open%20secret%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20these%20abductions%2C%20key%20arms%20of%20the%20state%20or%20military%20do%20not%20accept%20that%20they%20have%20abducted%20people.%20Major%20political%20parties%20seldom%20speak%20about%20the%20missing%20persons%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20they%20prefer%20to%20discuss%20the%20topic%20only%20when%20election%20season%20is%20near.%20In%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20therefore%2C%20the%20parties%20that%20ignored%20the%20Eid%20protest%20may%20suddenly%20remember%20the%20issue%20of%20abduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESammi%20Baloch%20and%20her%20sister%20have%20spent%2014%20years%20looking%20for%20their%20father%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESammi%20Baloch%2C%2023%2C%20activist%20and%20daughter%20of%20Dr%20Deen%20Muhammad%20Baloch%2C%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20her%20struggle.%20She%20did%20not%20choose%20this%20life%3B%20the%20unkind%20policies%20of%20Islamabad%20have%20dragged%20her%20and%20her%20sister%20Mehlab%20down%20this%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155514%2FSammi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155514%2FSammi.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155514%2FSammi-300x142.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155514%2FSammi-1024x486.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662391%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22569%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESammi%20Baloch.%20Photo%3A%20Veengas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESammi%20was%2011%20years%20old%20when%20she%20first%20heard%20the%20word%20abduction.%20But%20why%20was%20everyone%20so%20upset%20at%20home%3B%20why%20was%20her%20young%20mother%20mourning%3F%20She%20kept%20saying%20to%20herself%20that%20someone%20from%20the%20state%20had%20abducted%20her%20father%2C%20and%20would%20return%20him%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20days%20turned%20into%20months%3B%20months%20became%20years.%20Now%2C%2014%20years%20have%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20holding%20a%20presser%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20hold%20a%20mic%20as%20I%20was%20so%20confused%20and%20my%20hands%20were%20trembling%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sammi%20said%2C%20recalling%20her%20early%20days%20of%20struggle.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20can%20deliver%20a%20speech%20and%20this%20struggle%20has%20made%20me%20strong%20to%20bear%20the%20%3Cem%3Elathi%20charge%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20torture%20by%20the%20forces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20and%20her%20sister%20were%20very%20young%2C%20they%20did%20not%20know%20who%20to%20complain%20to%20or%20what%20to%20say.%20They%20memorised%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBain%20ul%20Aqwami%20Idare%3C%2Fem%3E%20(international%20organisations)%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupport%20has%20been%20hard%20to%20come%20by%2C%20she%20believes%2C%20and%20people%E2%80%99s%20cold%20behaviour%20is%20etched%20in%20her%20memory.%20She%20cannot%20forget%20how%20people%20avoided%20her%20or%20never%20responded%20to%20her%20messages%20asking%20them%20to%20raise%20their%20voices%20for%20her%20father.%20In%20fact%2C%20people%20still%20behave%20the%20same%2C%20she%20said%2C%20when%20she%20launched%20a%20social%20media%20campaign%20for%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20release.%20Those%20who%20do%20support%20them%2C%20she%20said%2C%20often%20pay%20the%20price%20%E2%80%93%20like%20her%20cousin%20who%20was%20allegedly%20tortured%20by%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20love%20talking%20about%20democracy%2C%20climate%20change%20and%20human%20rights%2C%20but%20the%20same%20circle%20of%20people%20will%20not%20talk%20about%20us%20%5Bthe%20Baloch%5D.%20They%20raise%20their%20voice%20for%20Palestine%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20for%20Balochistan%20their%20voices%20become%20silent.%20The%20reason%3A%20the%20Palestine%20and%20Kashmir%20issues%20suit%20the%20state%2C%20and%20the%20Balochistan%20issue%20is%20within%20the%20state.%20They%20only%20follow%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20not%20the%20real%20spirit%20of%20democratic%20values%20and%20human%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20sad%20that%20her%20struggle%20has%20not%20led%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20release.%20If%20her%20father%20had%20been%20picked%20up%20in%202023%2C%20not%20in%202009%2C%20she%20would%20have%20led%20a%20movement%20differently%2C%20she%20said%2C%20as%20she%20understands%20more%20now%20than%20she%20did%20as%20a%20girl%20who%20was%2011%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20alone%20in%20a%20fight%20for%20justice%2C%20other%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%20who%20share%20the%20same%20anguish%20are%20our%20strength%20and%20we%20support%20each%20other.%20Sorrows%20and%20struggles%20connect%20us%20more%20than%20any%20%5Bfamilial%5D%20relation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESammi%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20judicial%20system%2C%20saying%20that%20judges%20who%20collected%20their%20salaries%20from%20the%20state%20would%20hardly%20go%20against%20the%20system.%20Despite%20knowing%20the%20system%2C%20the%20kin%20of%20the%20Baloch%20missing%20persons%20approach%20judges%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20one%20day%20they%20will%20get%20justice.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20is%2C%20we%20know%20that%20it%20is%20impossible%20%E2%80%93%20justice%20for%20the%20Baloch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155751%2Fprotesters5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155751%2Fprotesters5.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155751%2Fprotesters5-300x142.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155751%2Fprotesters5-1024x486.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662393%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22569%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBaloch%20protesters%20at%20the%20Karachi%20Press%20Club.%20Photo%3A%20Veengas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Eid%20protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Eid%20this%20yeat%2C%20there%20were%20two%20countries%20in%20Pakistan.%20One%20was%20celebrating%20and%20posting%20pictures%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20another%20was%20protesting%20in%20different%20cities%20of%20Balochistan%20and%20Sindh%20and%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20missing%20persons.%20%E2%80%9CBring%20back%20our%20missing%20Eids%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20one%20poster%20at%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInaam%20Abbasi%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Sindh%20Sabha%20organisation%2C%20said%20that%20both%20provinces%20of%20Sindh%20and%20Balochistan%20had%20suffered%20and%20their%20natural%20resources%20had%20been%20stolen.%20He%20appreciated%20Baloch%20women%20and%20children%20who%20joined%20the%20protest%20on%20Eid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQazi%20Khizr%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20said%20that%20the%20state%20should%20not%20be%20expected%20to%20offer%20garlands%20when%20the%20state%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20disapp