3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDil%20se%20Open%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTogether%E2%80%9D%20includes%20its%20employees%3A%20Axis%20cares%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Crounded%20wellness%E2%80%9D%20of%20its%20employees%2C%20including%20their%20mental%20health.%20It%20carries%20out%20repeated%20surveys%3B%20it%20has%20enabled%20an%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%C2%A0%20bot%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9CHR%20%5BHuman%20resources%5D%20conversations%E2%80%9D%20with%20them%3B%20and%20it%20employs%20professional%20counsellors%20to%20support%20them%20at%20times%20of%20stress%20(600%20have%20been%20counselled%2C%20and%20another%201%2C247%20are%20waiting%20in%20queue%20for%20counselling).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20pity%2C%20then%2C%20that%20in%20this%20year%20of%20%E2%80%98openness%E2%80%99%2C%20Axis%20has%20actually%20reduced%20the%20information%20it%20earlier%20provided%20regarding%20employee%20attrition%20and%20declined%20to%20respond%20to%20queries%20on%20the%20subject.%20And%20in%20this%20year%20of%20%E2%80%98togetherness%E2%80%99%2C%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20its%20employees%20have%20exited%2C%20in%20a%20significant%20increase%20compared%20to%20FY2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Axis%20Bank%20board%20of%20directors%20boasts%20of%20former%20senior%20executives%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20as%20well%20as%20a%20nominee%20of%20Bain%20Capital.%20Moreover%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20board%20members%20declare%20a%20specialisation%20precisely%20in%20human%20resources%20management.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20board%20hardly%20mentions%20this%20massive%20annual%20exodus%20in%20its%20annual%20report%2C%20and%20chooses%20to%20remain%20silent%20on%20its%20causes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20the%20third%20element%20in%20the%20new%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9CWinning%E2%80%9D%2C%20Axis%20has%20no%20doubt%20won%20the%20prize%20for%20customer%20complaints%20in%20banks%20(as%20discussed%20in%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhemindrahazari.com%2F2023%2F06%2F20%2Fwill-citis-retail-customers-stick-with-axis-bank-the-private-sector-market-leader-in-customer-complaints%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earticle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20and%20perhaps%20it%20has%20done%20so%20for%20staff%20attrition%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EExtract%20of%20%E2%80%98open%E2%80%99%20theme%20in%20axis%20bank%E2%80%99s%20FY2023%20annual%20report%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20421px)%2085vw%2C%20421px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154338%2Funnamed.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22421%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154338%2Funnamed.png%20421w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154338%2Funnamed-181x300.png%20181w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662387%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22699%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Axis%20Bank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axisbank.com%2Fdocs%2Fdefault-source%2Fannual-reports%2Ffor-axis-bank%2Fannual-report-for-the-year-2022-2023.pdf%5C%22%3EFY2023%20Annual%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20annual%20report%20talks%20of%20the%20pivotal%20role%20of%20employees%20in%20achieving%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20long%20term%20goals%2C%20and%20boasts%20that%20its%20policies%20focus%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Crounded%20wellness%E2%80%9D%20of%20its%20staff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154722%2Funnamed-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221097%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154722%2Funnamed-1.png%201097w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154722%2Funnamed-1-300x168.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154722%2Funnamed-1-1024x573.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Axis%20Bank%20FY2023%20Annual%20Report%20p.%20135%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20such%20public%20displays%20of%20devotion%20to%20employee%20welfare%2C%20one%20would%20expect%20the%20nearly%2092%2C000%20permanent%20staff%20members%20of%20the%20bank%20to%20display%20loyalty%20to%20their%20employer.%20However%2C%20similar%20tall%20claims%20regarding%20customer%20satisfaction%20made%20in%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20FY2022%20annual%20report%20later%20proved%20illusory%2C%20as%20Axis%20Bank%20emerged%20the%20private%20sector%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhemindrahazari.com%2F2023%2F06%2F20%2Fwill-citis-retail-customers-stick-with-axis-bank-the-private-sector-market-leader-in-customer-complaints%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emarket%20leader%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20in%20customer%20complaints.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20data%20in%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20FY2023%20annual%20report%20disclose%20that%2C%20far%20from%20displaying%20loyalty%2C%20Axis%20staff%20continued%20to%20leave%20in%20droves%20during%20the%20year.%20Staff%20attrition%20increased%20to%2034.8%25%20in%20FY2023%20from%2031.6%25%20in%20FY2022.%20The%20fact%20that%20more%20than%20a%20third%20(30%2C902)%20of%20the%20workforce%20exited%20in%20FY2023%2C%20up%20from%2025%2C960%20in%20FY2022%2C%20provides%20the%20real%20picture%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20public%20commitment%20to%20its%20labour%20force.%20This%20will%20have%20an%20adverse%20and%20consequential%20impact%20on%20customer%20service%20and%20banking%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%2075%2C029%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20employees%20have%20exited%20(voluntarily%20and%20involuntarily)%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years.%20That%20is%20as%20much%20as%2081%25%20of%20its%20headcount%20in%20FY2023%20and%2096%25%20of%20its%20headcount%20in%20FY2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bank%E2%80%99s%20attrition%20percentage%20in%20FY2023%20is%20its%20second%20highest%20since%20FY2018.%20With%20record%20customer%20complaints%20in%20FY2022%20and%20such%20a%20high%20churn%20in%20staff%2C%20which%20will%20be%20mainly%20at%20the%20entry%20and%20mid-management%20level%2C%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20entire%20retail%20strategy%20maybe%20in%20peril.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENote%3A%20Attrition%20in%20%25%20calculated%20based%20on%20average%20headcount%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154957%2Funnamed-2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154957%2Funnamed-2.png%20608w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09154957%2Funnamed-2-300x135.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22273%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENote%3A%20Attrition%20in%20%25%20calculated%20based%20on%20average%20headcount.%20Source%3A%20Axis%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bank%20also%20discusses%20its%20commitment%20to%20its%20female%20staff%20in%20the%20annual%20report%20and%20how%20its%20objective%20is%20to%20reach%2030%25%20female%20representation%20by%20FY2027%20from%2026%25%20in%20FY2023%2C%20and%20a%20targeted%2027%25%20during%20FY2024.%20It%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20Axis%20Bank%20plans%20to%20gradually%20increase%20female%20participation%20in%20its%20work%20force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20less%20noteworthy%20is%20that%20in%20the%20last%203%20years%2C%20female%20staff%20attrition%20has%20been%20higher%20than%20male%20attrition.%20Apparently%2C%20women%20employees%2C%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20do%20not%20feel%20happy%20at%20Axis%20Bank.%20Female%20attrition%20in%20percentage%20terms%20is%20the%20highest%20since%20FY2018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20465px)%2085vw%2C%20465px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155310%2Funnamed-3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22465%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155310%2Funnamed-3.png%20465w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155310%2Funnamed-3-300x177.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09155310%2Funnamed-3-425x250.png%20425w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662390%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22275%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENote%3A%20Attrition%20in%20%25%20calculated%20based%20on%20average%20headcount%3Cbr%3ESource%3A%20Axis%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20FY2018%20till%20FY2022%2C%20Axis%20Bank%20was%20an%20industry%20leader%20in%20voluntarily%20disclosing%20data%20on%20employees%20and%20attrition%2C%20which%20was%20highly%20commendable.%20Stakeholders%20could%20compute%20attrition%20in%20various%20categories%20by%20age%20bucket%2C%20management%20cadre%2C%20gender%20and%20even%20in%20new%20hires.%20The%20extensive%20