0Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20is%20scheduled%20to%20play%20at%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Bangalore%20and%20Kolkata.%20The%20ICC%20has%20also%20accepted%20that%20if%20the%20Pakistani%20national%20cricket%20team%20makes%20it%20to%20the%20semi-final%2C%20it%20will%20not%20play%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20but%20go%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhome%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Pakistani%20minister%20for%20Inter-Provincial%20Coordination%2C%20Ehsanur%20Rehman%20Mazari%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20look%20at%20all%20the%20issues%20surrounding%20the%20cricket%20team%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India.%20The%20Special%20Assistant%20to%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Tariq%20Fatemi%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20coordinator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMazari%20added%20that%20committee%20members%20would%20make%20recommendations%20regarding%20the%20Pakistan%20team%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20but%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20matter%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20taken%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20House%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20in%20his%20personal%20opinion%2C%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20cricket%20team%20should%20be%20reciprocal%20%E2%80%93%20if%20the%20Indian%20team%20had%20Asia%20Cup%20matches%20on%20Pakistani%20soil%2C%20it%20would%20do%20the%20same%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%20But%2C%20if%20India%20was%20playing%20in%20a%20third%20country%2C%20then%20Pakistan%20should%20also%20demand%20a%20similar%20option%2C%20Mazari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistani%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20and%20other%20wings%20of%20the%20government%20were%20carrying%20out%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20diligence%20as%20part%20of%20a%20routine%20process%20before%20it%20gives%20the%20green%20light%20for%20team%20Pakistan%20to%20fly%20to%20I