20causing%20death%2C%20suffering%2C%20destruction%20and%20displacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20security%20forces%20and%20their%20proxies%20in%20the%20settlements%20and%20far-right%20movements%20have%20committed%20summary%20executions%2C%20abductions%2C%20torture%20and%20other%20atrocities%20in%20Palestine%2C%20including%20the%20massacres%20of%20civilians%20in%20cities%2C%20towns%20and%20villages%2C%20and%20are%20implementing%20a%20policy%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%20apartheid.%20Israel%20continues%20to%20persistently%20violate%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20UN%20Charter%20through%20its%20acts%20of%20aggression%20against%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20independence%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20Palestine%2C%20and%20to%20blatantly%20and%20grossly%20violate%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20inter%20alia%20by%20deliberately%20targeting%20civilian%20structures%20that%20should%20not%20be%20the%20object%20of%20attack.%20These%20crimes%20reflect%20a%20grotesque%20indifference%20to%20the%20rules%20and%20laws%20of%20war%20that%20constrain%20the%20exercise%20of%20military%20power%2C%20as%20seen%20for%20instance%20in%20the%20inhumane%20treatment%20of%20prisoners%20of%20war%2C%20the%20widespread%20use%20of%20torture%20and%20the%20summary%20executions%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20denial%20of%20free%20access%20for%20international%20humanitarian%20organisations%20and%20journalists%20to%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20to%20the%20Israeli%20military%20courts%20and%20to%20prisons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20State%20Repression%20and%20Its%20Justification%2C%20India%20and%20Israel%20Have%20Much%20in%20Common%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Findia-israel-palestine-kashmir-azad-ressa%5C%22%3EIn%20State%20Repression%20and%20Its%20Justification%2C%20India%20and%20Israel%20Have%20Much%20in%20Common%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20is%20to%20terrorise%20the%20Palestinian%20population%2C%20to%20extend%20the%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%20to%20force%20the%20Palestinians%20to%20accept%20the%20occupying%20power%20and%20agree%20to%20the%20illegal%20Israeli%20annexation%20of%20several%20parts%20of%20Palestine%20or%20all%20of%20it%2C%20under%20one%20apartheid%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20policy%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%20apartheid%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20deliberate%20actions%20are%20causing%20a%20food%20crisis%20in%20Palestinian%20farming%20and%20pastoral%20communities%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20especially%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%20and%20southern%20Hebron%20hills%2C%20where%20many%20grazing%20and%20agricultural%20areas%20were%20declared%20closed%20to%20Palestinians%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20Jewish-only%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20carries%20out%20mass%20surveillance%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20population%2C%20including%20lawyers%2C%20human%20rights%20activists%20and%20journalists%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20destroying%20the%20social%20fabric%20and%20preventing%20any%20independent%20or%20oppositional%20thought%20and%20movement.%20Israel%20is%20also%20waging%20an%20active%20information%20war%2C%20spreading%20disinformation%20about%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20and%20political%20leadership%2C%20and%20conducting%20special%20operations%20to%20destabilise%20society%20in%20Palestine%20and%20discredit%20Palestine%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20its%20international%20partners%2C%20including%20by%20the%20Israeli%20minister%20of%20defence%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20that%20six%20Palestinian%20human%20rights%20organisations%20are%20terrorist%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09124216%2FF0g_YhoXsAESr5h.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09124216%2FF0g_YhoXsAESr5h.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09124216%2FF0g_YhoXsAESr5h-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662368%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Jenin%20refugee%20camp%20which%20was%20recently%20raided%20and%20destroyed%20by%20Israeli%20forces.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40UNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20illegally%20annexed%20East%20Jerusalem%20and%20implemented%20there%20a%20policy%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%20apartheid.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20illegal%20actions%20in%20East%20Jerusalem%20include%20extensive%20house%20demolitions%2C%20the%20mass%20deportation%20of%20Palestinian%20families%20from%20their%20homes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20cancelation%20of%20residence%20permits%20for%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20and%20their%20proxies%20in%20the%20settlements%20and%20in%20the%20far-right%20militias%20have%20repeatedly%20targeted%20Palestinian%20civilians%3B%20violent%20groups%20of%20the%20settlers%20and%20the%20far-right%20receive%20significant%20political%2C%20economic%20and%20logistical%20support%20from%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20in%20particular%20from%20the%20Israel%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20and%20Israel%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20years%20Israel%20has%20supported%20and%20financed%2C%20directly%20and%20indirectly%2C%20terrorist%20groups%20of%20the%20settlers%20and%20the%20far-right%2C%20and%20it%20allowed%20them%20to%20operate%20freely.%20Supporters%20of%20genocide%2C%20ethnic%20cleansing%2C%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20war%20crimes%20and%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CKach%E2%80%9D%20movement%20(which%20was%20recognised%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20US%2C%20EU%2C%20Canada%2C%20Japan%20and%20Israel%20itself)%20are%20senior%20ministers%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20new%20government%20and%20are%20members%20of%20its%20coalition%20in%20the%20Knesset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Israeli%20apartheid%20regime%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20political%20alliance%20with%20the%20far-right%2C%20since%20his%20second%20government%20in%202009%20there%20has%20been%20an%20exponential%20growth%20in%20Israeli-Jewish%20terrorist%20incidents%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20Among%20other%20things%2C%20dozens%20of%20churches%20and%20mosques%20were%20set%20on%20fire%20or%20vandalised%2C%20hundreds%20of%20residences%20and%20businesses%20and%20thousands%20of%20vehicles%20were%20set%20on%20fire%2C%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20olive%20trees%20were%20cut%20down.%20In%20addition%2C%20as%20described%2C%20countless%20Palestinian%20civilians%20have%20been%20attacked%2C%20beaten%2C%20shot%2C%20kidnapped%2C%20tortured%2C%20threatened%20and%20even%20murdered%20by%20far-right%20Israeli%20terrorist%20operatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20sixth%20Netanyahu%20government%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20there%20were%20countless%20acts%20of%20terrorism%20by%20Israeli%20far-right%20terrorists%2C%20but%20they%20were%20usually%20carried%20out%20in%20small%20groups%20and%20many%20times%20by%20masked%20people%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20darkness.%20Because%20of%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20current%20government%20and%20coalition%2C%20the%20terrorists%20of%20the%20far-right%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20reason%20to%20hide%20and%20they%20carry%20out%20a%20chain%20of%20pogroms%20with%20the%20participation%20of%20between%20several%20dozen%20to%20several%20hundred%20in%20each%20pogrom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Does%20Modi's%20India%20Care%20About%20Palestine%20Any%20More%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnarendra-modi-india-palestine%5C%22%3EDoes%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%20Care%20About%20Palestine%20Any%20More%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20on%20February%2026%2C%202023%2C%20there%20was%20a%20pogrom%20in%20Hawara%20in%20which%20approximately%20400%20terrorists%20from%20the%20Israeli%20far-right%20participated.%20They%20even%20received%20support%20from%20Knesset%20members%20in%20the%20coalition%20and%20senior%20ministers%20in%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20government.%20Although%20we%20submitted%20a%20demand%20to%20the%20Attorney%20General%20to%20open%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20against%20those%20politicians%20who%20incited%20the%20pogroms%20and%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20erasure%20of%20the%20Hawara%20village%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20one%20MK%2C%20no%20criminal%20investigation%20was%20opened%20and%20thus%20the%20incitement%20continued%20in%20the%20chain%20of%20pogroms%20since%20then.%20Last%20week%2C%20pogroms%20were%20carried%20out%20in%20Turmus%20Ayya%2C%20in%20Al-Lubban%20ash-Sharqiya%20and%20other%20villages%2C%20when%20crowds%20of%20terrorists%20from%20the%20Israeli%20far-right%20carried%20out%20their%20plot%20openly%20without%20the%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20intervening%20or%20arresting%20them.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20received%20reports%20upon%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20Israeli%20terrorists%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20villages%2C%20and%20the%20area%20is%20also%20covered%20with%20a%20dense%20network%20of%20security%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20in%20the%20chain%20of%20pogroms%20there%20were%20only%20a%20few%20incidents%20of%20killing%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20being%20responsible%20again%20for%20the%20Sabra%20and%20Shatila%20massacre%20%E2%80%93%20only%20this%20time%20it%20will%20not%20be%20done%20by%20armed%20militias%20of%20the%20Christian%20far-right%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20but%20by%20armed%20militias%20of%20the%20Israeli%20far-right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20aforementioned%2C%20we%2C%20a%20coalition%20of%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20organisations%20and%20movements%20%E2%80%93%20Looking%20the%20Occupation%20in%20the%20Eye%2C%20Machsom%20Watch%2C%20New%20Profile%2C%20Combatants%20for%20Peace%2C%20Jahalin%20Solidarity%2C%20Jordan%20Valley%20Activists%20and%20Jewish-Israeli%20Dissent%20(JID)%20Leipzig%20%E2%80%93%20asked%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20act%20according%20to%20Chapter%20VII%20of%20the%20Charter%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20and%20to%20establish%20a%20mission%20of%20the%20UN%20to%20ensure%20effective%20protection%20for%20the%20civilian%20Palestinian%20population%20from%20targeted%20attacks%20by%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20and%20Israeli%20far-right%20militias%20and%20settlers%2C%20with%20respect%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20human%20rights%20and%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%20Such%20a%20UN%20mission%20for%20protecting%20civilians%20was%20established%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%20(MONUSCO).%20We%20also%20asked%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20impose%20sanctions%2C%20including%20travel%20bans%20and%20assets%20freeze%20on%20Israeli%20individuals%20and%20entities%20that%20are%20responsible%20for%2C%20or%20complicit%20in%2C%20or%20having%20engaged%20in%20%E2%80%93%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20%E2%80%93%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20especially%20during%20the%20pogroms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20endless%20failures%20of%20the%20UN%20and%20its%20representatives%20for%20decades%20to%20protect%20the%20Palestinian%20population%2C%20and%20also%20of%20the%20UN%20missions%20around%20the%20world%20and%20specifically%20in%20the%20DRC%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20it%20is%20better%20for%20the%20UN%20to%20protect%20the%20Palestinians%20than%20to%20trust%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20to%20adhere%20to%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEitay%20Mack%20is%20a%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20and%20activist%20based%20in%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688891408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F09124043%2FF0g-2YqWYAAx770.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Funsc-must-act-to-protect-palestinian-residents-of-west-bank-from-attacks-pogroms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Because%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Israeli%20apartheid%20regime%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20Netanyahu's%20political%20alliance%20with%20the%20far-right%2C%20since%20his%20second%20government%20in%202009%20there%20has%20been%20an%20exponential%20growth%20in%20Israeli-Jewish%20terrorist%20incidents%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22https%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Funsc-must-act-to-protect-palestinian-residents-of-west-bank-from-attacks-pogroms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%2076%20died%2C%20133%20injured%20due%20to%20heavy%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688890691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101611464%2Cimgsize-299470.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fat-least-76-died-133-injured-due-to-heavy-in-pakistan%2Farticleshow%2F101611477.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101611477.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22https%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%