r%20landing%20on%20the%20moon%20possibly%20by%20the%20last%20week%20of%20August.%20The%20date%20is%20decided%20by%20the%20sunrise%20on%20the%20moon.%20When%20the%20landing%20takes%20place%2C%20sunlight%20has%20to%20be%20there.%20A%20day%20on%20the%20moon%20is%2015%20Earth%20days.%20You%20will%20have%20sunlight%20for%2015%20days%20and%20in%20the%20next%2015%20days%20there%20will%20be%20no%20sunlight%20for%20a%20given%20location%2C%E2%80%9D%20Somanath%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20meeting%20on%20the%20space%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20third%20lunar%20mission.%20As%20everyone%20waits%20with%20bated%20breath%20for%20the%20launch%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20a%20brief%20history%20of%20Chandrayaan-2%20and%20Chandrayaan-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAnnouncing%20the%20launch%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%F0%9F%9A%80LVM3-M4%2FChandrayaan-3%20%F0%9F%9B%B0%EF%B8%8FMission%3A%3Cbr%3EThe%20launch%20is%20now%20scheduled%20for%20%3Cbr%3E%F0%9F%93%86July%2014%2C%202023%2C%20at%202%3A35%20pm%20IST%20%3Cbr%3Efrom%20SDSC%2C%20Sriharikota%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EStay%20tuned%20for%20the%20updates!%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1676918082265321472%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-2%3A%20A%20stepping%20stone%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20416px)%20100vw%2C%20416px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchandrayaan2-1688735226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22416%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20file%20image%20of%20Chandrayaan%202%20lift%20off%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2