method%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20follow%20a%20series%20of%20steps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soil%20of%20the%20potential%20forest%20is%20analysed%20and%20enhanced%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20rice%20husk.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20seedlings%20of%20local%20trees%2C%20herbs%20and%20shrubs%20are%20planted%20randomly%20in%20this%20soil%20and%20in%20close%20clusters%20such%20as%2030%2C000%20per%20hectare.%20The%20next%20three%20years%20that%20follow%20are%20crucial%20as%20the%20area%20is%20monitored%20and%20weeded%20frequently.%20Due%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259236%2Ffood-forests-george-remedios-mumbai-pune-green-turning-tide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edensity%20of%20the%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E%20(compared%20to%201%2C000%20per%20hectare%20in%20a%20commercial%20forest)%2C%20the%20trees%20begin%20to%20compete%20for%20resources%20and%20this%20encourages%20faster%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forest%20begins%20to%20thrive%20and%20is%20then%20left%20to%20grow%20naturally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mangaluru%2C%20Jeeth%20has%20been%20successful%20in%20introducing%20the%20Miyawaki%20concept%20along%20the%20National%20Highway%20and%20in%20areas%20like%20Nanthoor%2C%20Gurupura%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Polytechnic%20College%20and%20Nandigudda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20he%20did%20it%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20chose%20170%20varieties%20and%20species%20of%20trees%2C%20herbs%20and%20shrubs.%20My%20intention%20was%20to%20grow%20food%20forests%20using%20the%20Miyawaki%20method.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255198%2Fodisha-women-tribal-system-kodarapalli-thengapalli-forest-protection-environment-natural-resources-over-exploitation-guard-conservation-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20forests%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20open%20for%20all%20species%20to%20