n%20involved%20in%20play%20and%20sport%20as%20part%20of%20their%20core%20education.%20For%20roughly%20its%20first%20decade%2C%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20organisation%20worked%20with%20private%20schools%20that%20were%20able%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20sports%20and%20physical%20education%20programmes.%20Now%2C%20Sportz%20Village%20operates%20in%2022%20states%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20does%20significant%20work%20in%20rural%20areas%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20play%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoumil%20explains%20that%20over%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20he%20had%20tried%20multiple%20models%20of%20getting%20children%20to%20play%20in%20sustainable%20and%20scalable%20ways%20before%20arriving%20on%20the%20school%20partnership%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProviding%20adults%20%E2%80%94%20who%20control%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20place%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20right%20data%20and%20visibility%20around%20the%20process%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20the%20impact%20on%20goals%20that%20they%20care%20about%20(attendance%2C%20grades%2C%20fitness%2C%20sports%2C%20and%20so%20on)%20can%20help%20get%20100%20million%20children%20to%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20notes%2C%20is%20possible%20through%20a%20structured%20programme%20that%20integrates%20with%20the%20school%20PE%20timetable%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313823%2Fviral-video-of-playground-under-navi-mumbai-flyover-inspires-other-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesigned%20for%20limited%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20time%2C%20and%20provides%20resources%2C%20data%2C%20and%20visibility%20to%20the%20various%20stakeholders%20involved.%20Most%20of%20all%2C%20it%20gets%20%E2%80%9C100%25%20of%20the%20children%20to%20develop%20the%20right%20fitness%2C%20skills%2C%20and%20attitudes%20to%20play%20for%20life%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20the%20organisation%20launched%20Sportz%20Village%20Foundation%20to%20help%20raise%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20funds%20and%20expand%20its%20outreach%20in%20government%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCl0uwNprWc-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCl0uwNprWc-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCl0uwNprWc-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Sportz%20Village%20Foundation%20(%40sportzvillagefoundation)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CSR%20law%20requires%20a%20corporate%20to%20invest%20only%20with%20a%20non-profit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gill%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20new%20structure%20was%20important%20so%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20constraints%20in%20raising%20funds%20for%20running%20programmes%20in%20government%20schools.%20The%20Foundation%20also%20allows%20us%20to%20achieve%20different%20goals%2C%20even%20though%20the%20structure%20of%20our%20programme%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20experience%20for%20children%20is%20uniform%20in%20private%20and%20public%20schools.%20In%20government%20schools%20that%20cater%20to%20children%20from%20underserved%20communities%2C%20there%20are%20different%20things%20ailing%20the%20system%E2%80%A6the%20biggest%20piece%20is%20the%20socio-emotional%20skills.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20examples%20of%20socio-emotional%20skills%20are%20the%20ability%20to%20understand%20your%20thoughts%20and%20feelings%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20relate%20to%20others.%20These%20skills%20are%20widely%20recognised%20as%20vital%20to%20personal%20development%20and%20building%20healthy%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E50%2C000%20lives%20transformed%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%20says%20that%20keeping%20children%2C%20especially%20girls%2C%20in%20school%20was%20another%20one%20of%20their%20priorities%2C%20as%20the%20drop-out%20rate%20in%20government%20schools%20is%20quite%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%2C%20which%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Sport%20for%20Change%E2%80%99%2C%20functions%20at%20three%20levels.%20At%20the%20base%20is%20sports%20education%2C%20which%20involves%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316259%2Fanantapur-sports-academy-helps-rural-andhra-children-study-earn-livelihood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20children%20basic%20physical%20and%20sports%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20core%20%5Bof%20the%20programme%5D%20was%20to%20integrate%20children%20in%20play%20and%20sport%20because%20it%20was%20central%20to%20their%20experience%20and%20development%20process%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20be%20athletes%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gill%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Upma%20Kanswa%20Jain%2C%20who%20manages%20marketing%20and%20communication%20for%20the%20Foundation%2C%20over%2050%2C000%20students%20are%20currently%20engaged%20in%20their%20programmes%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey%20also%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20pathway%20for%20those%20who%20performed%20well%20in%20a%20sport%20and%20wished%20to%20pursue%20it%20further.%20So%2C%20the%20next%20level%20is%20their%20sports%20excellence%20programme%20PathwayZ%2C%20where%20interested%20or%20selected%20children%20are%20given%20expert%20training%20in%20their%20sports%20development%20centres%20(SDC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fkabaddi-1688110426.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kabaddi%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fkabaddi-1688110426.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fkabaddi-1688110426-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fkabaddi-1688110426-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fkabaddi-1688110426-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fkabaddi-1688110426-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322291%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESportz%20Village%20operates%20in%2022%20states.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20centres%20are%20located%20within%20the%20schools%20in%20which%20they%20work.%20At%20the%20highest%20level%2C%20they%20take%20the%20best-performing%20student-athletes%20from%20the%20SDCs%20and%20admit%20them%20into%20the%20high-performance%20learning%20centres%20(HPLC)%2C%20where%20they%20are%20also%20provided%20with%20match%20and%20tournament%20opportunities%2C%20and%20given%20scouting%20information%20about%20district%2C%20state%2C%20and%20national%20selection%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2050%2C000%20students%20in%20their%20programmes%2C%20over%202%2C200%20are%20enrolled%20in%20sports%20development%20centres%2C%20with%20roughly%2060%25%20being%20boys%20and%20the%20rest%20girls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20there%20are%20about%2040%20students%20in%20their%20high-performance%20learning%20centre%2C%20of%20which%20roughly%20half%20are%20boys%20and%20half%20are%20girls.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20get%20invited%20to%20trials%20that%20are%20happening%20at%20the%20district%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jain%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20perform%2C%20then%20state%20level%2C%20then%20national%20level%20events.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShaping%20athletes%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDifferent%20geographical%20areas%20offer%20different%20sports%20depending%20on%20the%20infrastructure%20available%20in%20the%20schools.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20Noida%2C%20children%20can%20choose%20between%20volleyball%2C%20cricket%2C%20football%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekabaddi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20athletics.%20The%20sports%20development%20centres%20operate%20six%20days%20a%20week%20and%20host%20sessions%20lasting%20two%20hours%20a%20day.%20Depending%20on%20the%20school%2C%20the%20sessions%20are%20held%20either%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20in%20the%20evening.%20The%20children%20are%20given%20t-shirts%2C%20shorts%2C%20shoes%20and%20additional%20nutrition%20in%20the%20form%20of%20bananas%2C%20eggs%20and%20milk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20situations%20where%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20parents%20are%20reluctant%20to%20let%20them%20attend%20the%20sports%20programmes%2C%20the%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20programme%20managers%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20parents%20to%20tell%20them%20how%20good%20their%20child%20is%20at%20sports%2C%20and%20that%20everything%20is%20paid%20for%2C%20so%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20any%20additional%20expenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ranvijay%20Gupta%2C%20one%20of%20the%20programme%20managers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Foundation%20has%20faced%20the%20odd%20protest%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9C%5BThe%20parents%5D%20tell%20us%2C%20%E2%80%98You%20people%20are%20spoiling%20our%20kids%20by%20making%20them%20go%20outside%20and%20play.%20This%20is%20not%20our%20culture.%20We%20cannot%20let%20them%20go%20outside%20and%20play%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20change%20the%20minds%20of%20even%20these%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20takes%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20take%20the%20help%20of%20the%20other%20parents%20whose%20children%20are%20in%20the%20programme.%20I%20tell%20them%20to%20come%20and%20support%20us.%20We%20have%20a%20second%20meeting%2C%20and%20a%20third%20meeting.%20After%20that%2C%20we%20can%20mostly%20convince%20them%2C%20and%20they%20send%20their%20wards%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20his%20experience%2C%20around%2070%25%20of%20the%20responses%20they%20get%20from%20parents%20are%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCizR0FFrYBF%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCizR0FFrYBF%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCizR0FFrYBF%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Sportz%20Village%20Foundation%20(%40sportzvillagefoundation)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20(38)%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20programmes%20in%20Lucknow%20%26amp%3B%20Noida-based%20schools%20supported%20by%20the%20HCL%20Foundation.%20He%20joined%20Sportz%20Village%20in%202010%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20Foundation%20in%202017.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20they%20had%20just%205%20to%2010%20girls%20in%20their%20SDCs%20when%20they%20started%20the%20programme%2C%20but%20now%20they%20work%20with%20over%20600%20girls%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20helped%20more%20than%20450%20children%20play%20in%20district-level%20tournaments%2C%20more%20than%20100%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%20and%20over%2030%20at%20the%20national%20level%20to%20date%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20very%20satisfying%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20role%20models%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20girls%20is%20Rukhsar%2C%20a%20Class%2011%20student%20at%20Govt.%20Girls%20Inter%20College%20Vikash%20Nagar%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20She%20is%20an%20avid%20%3Cem%3Ekabaddi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplayer%20and%20wants%20to%20represent%20India%20one%20day.%20However%2C%20previously%2C%20her%20circumstances%20held%20her%20back.%20Her%20father%20earns%20Rs%207%2C000%20a%20month%20working%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20and%20did%20not%20support%20her%20desire%20to%20be%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekabaddi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplayer%2C%20though%20her%20mother%20and%20three%20siblings%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sports%20for%20Change%20programme%20cleared%20the%20way%20for%20her%20to%20play%20by%20giving%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298431%2Fwest-bengal-brothers-use-football-and-academics-to-empower-village-girls-shreeja-ngo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20opportunity%20to%20train%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20expert%20coaches%20and%20sports%20nutritionists%2C%20while%20also%20learning%20life%20skills%20such%20as%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20in%20just%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20Rukhsar%20has%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20senior%20women%E2%80%99s%20state%20and%20junior%20girl%E2%80%99s%20state%20%3Cem%3Ekabaddi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eteams.%20She%20is%20also%20a%20promising%20athlete%20in%20the%20triple%20jump%2C%20where%20she%20finished%20first%20at%20the%20district%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20feel%20much%20better%20now%20because%20I%20am%20travelling%20to%20different%20places%2C%20meeting%20new%20people%20and%20my%20game%20is%20getting%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rukhsar%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20hires%20specialised%20coaches%20to%20run%20its%20sports%20excellence%20programmes.%20The%20coaches%20must%20have%20played%20at%20the%20state%20level%20in%20their%20sport%20and%20hold%20a%20minimum%20qualification%20of%20a%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20Education.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20organisation%20has%20grown%2C%20hiring%20good%20coaches%20has%20become%20a%20constraint%20because%20funds%20have%20not%20kept%20pace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20c