E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESportz%20Village%20Foundation%20has%20conducted%20a%20number%20of%20studies%20to%20determine%20the%20impact%20of%20its%20programmes%20on%20education%2C%20health%20and%20empowerment.%20One%20of%20them%20concluded%20that%20in%20the%20roughly%20390%20schools%20supported%20by%20Ashok%20Leyland%2C%20the%20children%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportzvillagefoundation.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FSports_In_Education_CSR_AshokLeyland.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20likely%20to%20attend%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20showed%20a%2010%25%20increase%20in%20fitness%20levels%2C%2018%20months%20after%20the%20programme%20was%20launched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20study%20with%20the%20Sports%20Authority%20of%20Gujarat%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportzvillagefoundation.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FWomen_Empowerment_through_Sport-Govt._of_Gujarat_Sportz_Village_Foundation-Case_Study.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemonstrated%20a%2023%25%20increase%20in%20female%20participation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20after-school%20programmes%2C%20two%20years%20after%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20conduct%20an%20annual%20health%20survey%2C%20of%20which%20the%20most%20recent%20results%20claim%20that%2095%25%20of%20children%20improved%20their%20fitness%20levels%2C%2092%25%20improved%20their%20communication%20abilities%20and%2078%25%20developed%20greater%20emotional%20capabilities%20in%20the%20face%20of%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20has%20set%20ambitious%20goals%20for%202023.%20It%20wants%20to%20add%20100%2C000%20children%20to%20its%20programmes%20and%20enable%20over%201%2C000%20student-athletes%20to%20perform%20at%20an%20elite%20level.%20Improving%20gender%20perception%20and%20inclusivity%20is%20another%20priority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20still%20some%20barriers%20in%20our%20society%20around%20gender%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20that%20at%20the%20policy%20level%2C%20inclusivity%20should%20equally%20be%20a%20focus%20so%20that%20more%20talented%20girls%20can%20come%20forward%20without%20any%20hesitation%2C%20participate%20in%20sports%20and%20eventually%20win%20medals%20for%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNurturing%20athletes%2C%20especially%20girls%2C%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20way%20to%20create%20role%20models%20for%20children%20and%20youth%20of%20India%2C%20within%20and%20beyond%20the%20field%20of%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gill%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688122053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fsportz-village-1688110251.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D322281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saumil%20Majmudar%20and%20Parminder%20Gill%20run%20Sportz%20Village%2C%20Bengaluru-based%20organisation%20that%20uses%20sports%20and%20play%20to%20encourage%20children%20in%20rural%20areas%20to%20stay%20in%20school.%20They%20have%20also%20helped%20students%20become%20athletes%20playing%20at%20district%2C%20state%20and%20national%20levels%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20sports.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22http%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322281%2Fbengaluru-duo-uses-sports-to-help-rural-girls-study-in-school-sportz-village%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bed%20Bath%20%26%20Beyond%20To%20Stay%20Online%20After%20Overstock.com%20Buys%20Rights%20To%20Bankrupt%20Retailer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Overstock.com%20acquired%20the%20bankrupt%20retail%20chain%E2%80%99s%20intellectual%20property%20assets%20for%20%2421.5%20million%20and%20is%20dumping%20its%20name%20online.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688060818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F649dc10b2200003b00412fc0.jpeg%3Fcache%3DiguPYGXMfM%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fap-us-overstock-bed-bath-beyond_n_649dc108e4b028e6472f8629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Overstock.com%20acquired%20the%20bankrupt%20retail%20chain%E2%80%99s%20intellectual%20property%20assets%20for%20%2421.5%20million%20and%20is%20dumping%20its%20name%20online.%22%2C%22topic%22%3A%22http%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A380%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fap-us-overstock-bed-bath-beyond_n_649dc108e4b028e6472f8629%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fap-us-overstock-bed-bath-beyond_n_649dc108e4b028e6472f8629%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fap-us-overstock-bed-bath-beyond_n_649dc108e4b028e6472f8629%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT%20Delhi%20Grad%C2%A0Quit%20His%C2%A0High-Paying%20Corporate%20Job%20to%20Pursue%20UPSC%C2%A0Dream%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20long-standing%20joke%20of%20Indian%20parents%20wanting%20their%20children%20to%20bag%20that%20%3Cem%3Esarkari%20naukari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(government%20job)%20was%20a%20reality%20for%20the%20now%2025-year-old%20Robin%20Bansal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20able%20to%20bring%20this%20dream%20to%20reality%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F292435%2Fias-officer-namrata-jain-shares-tips-for-preparation-30-days-before-upsc-cse-prelims%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresults%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecame%20out%20this%20year.%20Clearing%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20exams%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Robin%20secured%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20135%20in%20his%20fourth%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20was%20not%20Robin%E2%80%99s%20first%20attempt%20at%20cracking%20an%20important%20exam.%20Before%20attempting%20his%20civil%20service%20exam%2C%20he%20had%20prepared%20and%20passed%20JEE%20in%202015%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310667%2Fvarun-khurana-iit-delhi-agritech-startup-otipy-helps-small-farmers-raise-income-sell-fresh-produce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20join%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20where%20he%20was%20placed%20in%20a%20high-paying%20job%20at%20Samsung%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20moment%20I%20got%20the%20job%2C%20I%20started%20to%20wonder%20if%20this%20really%20was%20my%20calling.%20Soon%2C%20I%20had%20this%20urge%20to%20quit%20and%20throw%20myself%20completely%20into%20the%20preparation%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReaching%20the%20last%20mile%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobin%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Lehragaga%20in%20the%20Sangrur%20district%20of%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20small%20town%2C%20I%20could%20see%20that%20it%20was%20only%20the%20civil%20servants%20who%20had%20the%20last%20mile%20reach%20in%20our%20country.%20If%20anything%20comes%20up%2C%20people%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%20small%20towns%20only%20have%20the%20government%20agencies%20to%20fall%20back%20on.%20So%20public%20service%20was%20always%20something%20that%20interested%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThanks%20to%20my%20parents%2C%20the%20seed%20for%20becoming%20a%20public%20servant%20was%20sown%20in%20my%20heart%20when%20I%20was%20just%20a%20child.%20So%20I%20always%20had%20an%20inclination%20towards%20the%20profession%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20try%20my%20hand%20at%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20schooling%20in%20his%20hometown%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297383%2Fmumbai-ojas-maheshwari-with-hearing-impairment-tops-iit-jee-advanced-shares-strategy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20cleared%20JEE%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20got%20admission%20to%20IIT%20Delhi%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGetting%20admission%20to%20IIT%20Delhi%20was%20great%20as%20I%20had%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20physics.%20I%20studied%20diligently%20in%20college.%20However%2C%20the%20urge%20to%20become%20a%20civil%20servant%20never%20died.%20Even%20when%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20will%20give%20the%20examination%20one%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-2-1-1687960148.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robin's%20parents%20sowed%20the%20seed%20of%20becoming%20a%20public%20servant%20when%20he%20was%20a%20child.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-2-1-1687960148.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-2-1-1687960148-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-2-1-1687960148-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-2-1-1687960148-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-2-1-1687960148-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322244%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERobin%E2%80%99s%20parents%20sowed%20the%20seed%20of%20becoming%20a%20public%20servant%20when%20he%20was%20a%20child.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20life%20was%20busy%20shaping%20a%20different%20path%20for%20Robin%2C%20he%20had%20already%20made%20up%20his%20mind%20about%20attempting%20UPSC%20CSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20graduating%20in%202019%2C%20I%20got%20placed%20in%20Samsung%20and%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru.%20While%20I%20was%20working%20there%2C%20I%20also%20started%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20exams%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSurely%2C%20the%20job%20was%20well%20paid%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20give%20me%20the%20satisfaction%20I%20was%20seeking.%20While%20I%20did%20start%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam%20while%20I%20was%20still%20working%2C%20I%20was%20not%20able%20to%20manage%20the%20timings%20and%20workload.%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20my%20100%20percent%20to%20the%20preparation%2C%20and%20therefore%20decided%20to%20quit%20the%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobin%20got%20a%20warm%20reception%20from%20his%20family%20on%20his%20decision%20to%20leave%20behind%20a%20high-paying%20job.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20was%20as%20happy%20as%20I%20was%20with%20my%20decision.%20They%20always%20wanted%20me%20to%20become%20a%20public%20servant%2C%20so%20they%20supported%20my%20decision%20wholeheartedly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Robin%20quit%20his%20corporate%20job%20and%20fully%20committed%20himself%20to%20preparing%20for%20UPSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20motivation%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20keep%20attempting%20the%20exam%20again%20and%20again%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20passion%20of%20becoming%20a%20public%20servant%20that%20kept%20pushing%20me%20to%20work%20harder.%20I%20could%20see%20that%20my%20grades%20were%20improving%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20if%20I%20focus%20more%2C%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20crack%20the%20exam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20cleared%20the%20CSE%2C%20Robin%20is%20keen%20on%20joining%20the%20Indian%20Police%20Services%2C%20given%20a%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98What%20I%20learnt%20along%20the%20way%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobin%2C%20who%20attempted%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%20three%20times%20before%20succeeding%20on%20his%20fourth%20attempt%2C%20emphasises%20the%20significance%20of%20learning%20from%20past%20mistakes.%20He%20provides%20valuable%20advice%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282477%2Fupsc-cse-syllabus-previous-years-question-paper-tips-ias-officer-anisha-shrivastav%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelpful%20tips%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20aspiring%20candidates%20aiming%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276282%2Fupsc-cse-topper-rallapalli-jagat-sai-tips-to-score-gs-interview-ias%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20to%20crack%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDetect%20your%20mistakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUPSC%20CSE%20is%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20exams%20to%20crack%20in%20India%2C%20and%20many%20times%2C%20it%20requires%20more%20than%20one%20attempt%20to%20clear%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20good%20thing%20about%20various%20attempts%20is%20that%20you%20can%20always%20figure%20out%20what%20went%20wrong%20in%20the%20failed%20attempt.%20The%20aspirants%20have%20so%20much%20space%20to%20learn%20if%20they%20have%20the%20right%20mindset%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearn%20from%20the%20mistakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20case%2C%20when%20I%20attempted%20the%20exam%20in%202019%2C%20I%20was%20not%20successful%20because%20I%20was%20not%20able%20to%20give%20my%20full%20attention%20to%20General%20Knowledge.%20I%20saw%20my%20shortcoming%2C%20so%20the%20next%20year%2C%20I%20worked%20hard%20to%20better%20myself%20in%20that%20category%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELearning%20is%20a%20continuous%20process%20and%20even%20if%20you%20fix%20one%20mistake%2C%20there%20is%20always%20a%20chance%20of%20committing%20another%20error.%20Robin%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20good%20at%20writing%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20practise%20writing%20fast%20and%20clearly.%20This%20I%20felt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20yet%20another%20failed%20attempt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-1-1687960019.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robin%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%20on%20his%20fourth%20attempt.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-1-1687960019.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-1-1687960019-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-1-1687960019-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-1-1687960019-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-1-1687960019-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERobin%20Bansal%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%20on%20his%20fourth%20attempt.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESelf-study%20or%20coaching%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20coaching%20has%20been%20helpful%20to%20many%20students%2C%20Robin%20has%20a%20countering%20view.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20package%20that%20the%20coaching%20centres%20provide%20to%20you%20is%20not%20always%20the%20best%20option.%20I%20had%20enrolled%20for%20coaching%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20really%20work%20for%20me.%20I%20suggest%20people%20have%20a%20good%20mix%20of%20both%20self-study%20and%20coaching%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%20depend%20on%20just%20the%20material%20your%20coaching%20centre%20provides%20you%20with.%20The%20syllabus%20of%20the%20exam%20is%20as%20vast%20as%20the%20sea%20and%20few%20notes%20cannot%20cover%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobin%20advises%20a%20judicious%20use%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20top%20recommended%20books%2C%20peer%20groups%20and%20other%20study%20materials%20for%20preparation.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20facing%20difficulties%20in%20a%20particular%20subject%2C%20then%20coaching%20would%20be%20a%20good%20option.%20Take%20help%20when%20needed%20for%20those%20subjects%20but%20also%20come%20back%20and%20self-study%2C%20and%20evaluate%20if%20those%20notes%20are%20enough%20for%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENever%20forget%20to%20solve%20the%20previous%20year%E2%80%99s%20papers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20cracking%20the%20exams%2C%20Robin%20opines%2C%20is%20by%20solving%20the%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20papers.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20aspirants%20get%20so%20indulged%20in%20covering%20the%20vast%20syllabus%20that%20they%20forget%20about%20the%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20papers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20mistake.%20The%20papers%20give%20a%20keen%20insight%20into%20the%20pattern%20of%20questions%20that%20can%20be%20asked%20in%20the%20current%20year.%20Solving%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20papers%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20tricks%20that%20helped%20me%20crack%20the%20exams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20care%20of%20your%20mental%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20syllabus%20of%20UPSC%20CSE%20is%20vast%20and%20the%20repeated%20attempts%20can%20be%20tedious.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20can%20be%20harrowing%20on%20your%20mental%20health%2C%20so%20it%20is%20important%20to%20address%20that.%20With%20failure%20comes%20a%20lot%20of%20self-doubt.%20This%20makes%20it%20very%20important%20to%20have%20a%20safe%20and%20peaceful%20environment%20around%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKeep%20yourself%20in%20a%20comfortable%20and%20loved%20environment.%20During%20the%20preparation%20for%20this%20attempt%2C%20I%20stayed%20with%20my%20family%20at%20home.%20Having%20people%20who%20love%20and%20support%20me%20helped%20me%20to%20keep%20a%20cool%20and%20sane%20mind%20throughout%20the%20preparation%20and%20examination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelax%20with%20your%20friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobin%20says%20that%20leisure%20time%20is%20also%20very%20important%20and%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20take%20breaks%20from%20studying%20and%20meet%20a%20few%20friends%20to%20relax%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20basics%20like%20practising%20hard%2C%20revising%20subjects%2C%20and%20learning%20new%20things%20that%20you%20are%20not%20familiar%20with%20are%20some%20aspects%20that%20most%20of%20us%20are%20aware%20of.%20However%2C%20what%20we%20forget%20is%20that%20it%20is%20very%20important%20to%20give%20yourself%20time%20to%20breathe%20and%20release%20pressure.%20I%20was%20lucky%20enough%20to%20have%20good%20friends%20who%20helped%20me%20during%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1687962274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fupsc-dream-2-1-1687960148.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%