face%20multiple%20challenges.%20They%20have%20to%20refill%20the%20water%20tanks%20constantly%2C%20and%20prolonged%20use%20leads%20to%20a%20humid%20atmosphere.%20Coolers%20are%20inefficient%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20device%20which%20would%20benefit%20these%20users%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sourish%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20inception%20of%20Zephyrus%2C%20which%20derived%20its%20name%20from%20the%20eponymous%20ancient%20Greek%20god%20of%20wind.%20This%2C%20they%20say%2C%20resonates%20with%20the%20device%E2%80%99s%20functions%20of%20both%20modes%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281434%2Fagra-data-scientist-builds-solar-power-eco-friendly-air-conditioner-exalta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20conditioning%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20cooling%20and%20heating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20the%20device%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshya%20explains%3A%20%E2%80%9CZephyrus%20is%20a%20two-in-one%20cooling%20and%20heating%20system%20powered%20by%20four%20cooling%20modules%20built%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20each%20of%20which%20is%20driven%20by%20a%20Peltier%20module%2C%20which%20is%20a%20small%20thermoelectric%20device%20sandwiched%20between%20two%20fin-shaped%20aluminium%20blocks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20electric%20current%20flows%20through%20this%20device%2C%20one%20side%20gets%20extremely%20hot%2C%20and%20the%20other%20side%20gets%20freezing%20cold.%20This%20creates%20a%20necessary%20temperature%20difference%20required%20to%20create%20the%20dual%20effect%20of%20cooling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fzephyrus-2-1687956192.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20a